hadiths[390]{hadithnumber,text}:
1,Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khala (peshab-pakhaney) ke liye jatey to (abadi sey) door chaley jatey.
2,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab peshab-pakhaney ki hajat hoti to (abadi sey) door chaley jatey yahan tak ke aap ko koi na dekh sakta.
3,"Abu-Tayyah kehtey hain ke mujhey eik Shekh ne bataya ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) jab Basra mein) bahaisiyat governer ( tashrif laye to log unhen Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se suni hui ahadis bayan kartey they. . . . . .) to us zimn mein) Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke naam eik khat likha jis mein un se kuch masayel daryaft kiye chunanche Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen jawab mein likha : main eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein tha, to aapney peshab kerney ka irada kya, pas aap eik deewar ki jad mein naram mitti ke paas aaye aur peshab kya. uskey baad aapney farmaya : ''tum mein se jab koi peshab karna chahey to uskey liye ( munasib naram ( jagah talash kar liya karey.''"
4,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khala (toilet) mein dakhil honey ka irada kartey to nichey likhi dua padhtey . ... Hammad bin Zaid ke alfaz hain : ( اللهم إني أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنَ الْخُبُثِ وَالْخَبَائِثِ (aur Abdul-Waris ke alfaz hain ( أَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ مِنَ الْخُبُثِ وَالْخَبَائِثِ ( ''aey Allah ! main khabis jinon aur jinniyon se teri panah mein aata hun.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Shoba Abdul-Azeez se ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ . . . . .) ke alfaz manqul hain jabke unhoney eik baar ( أَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ . . . . .) ke alfaz bhi bayan kiye. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Wuhaib se ( فَلْيَتَعَوَّذْ بِاللَّهِ ( ''usey Allah ki panah leni chahiye.'' ke alfaz manqul hain.
5,"Shoba Abdul-Azeez yani ibne-Suhaib sey, wo Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se yehi (mazkura baala ( hadees naqal kartey hain. unke alfaz ye hain : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ . . .) aur Shoba kehtey hain ke Abdul-Azeez ne ( Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey) eik baar ( أَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ . . . .) ke alfaz bayan kiye."
6,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''ye baitul-khala (toilet) jinon aur shetanon ke aaney janey ki jaghen hain, lihaza tum mein se jab koi baitul-khala (toilet) jana chahey to ye kalmaat keh liya karey : ( أَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ مِنَ الْخُبُثِ وَالْخَبَائِثِ ( ''main khabis jinon aur jinniyon (ke shar ( se Allah ki panah mein aata hun.''"
7,"Hazrat Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, kisi ne un se kaha ke tumharey Nabi ne to tumhen sabhi chizen sikhai hain yahan tak ke peshab-pakhaney ka tariqa bhi ! unhoney kaha : haan ! bila-shuba (us mein hamarey liye koi aeb ki baat nahin) aapney hamen peshab-pakhaney ke waqt qibla rukh honey aur daain haath se istinja kerney se mana farmaya hai aur ye ke ham mein se koi teen dhelon se kam mein istinja na karey aur gobar ya haddi se bhi istinja na karey."
8,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba main tumharey liye walid ki manind hun, tumhen sikhata hun. jab tum mein se koi pakhaney ke liye aaye to qibla rukh ho kar na bethey aur na qibley ki taraf pusht karey aur na daain haath se istinja karey.'' aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hukm diya kartey they ke (kam se kam ( teen dheley istimal kya keren aur gobar aur haddi se mana farmaya kartey they."
9,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se marfooan riwayat hai (yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ( ''jab tum baitul-khala (toilet) mein aao to peshab-pakhaney ke waqt qibley ki taraf munh na kya karo balke mashriq ya maghrib ki taraf rukh kya karo.'' ( Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke) jab ham shaam mein aaye to dekha ke) wahan ke) baitul-khala (toilet) qibla rukh par baney huey they, chunanche ham us se munh pher kar bethtey they aur istighfar kartey they."
10,"Hazrat Maaqil bin abi Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne peshab-pakhaney ke waqt qiblatain ( baitul-Haram aur baitul-Maqdis ( ki janib munh kerney se mana farmaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : '' Abu-Zaid, banu-Solba qabiley ke azad karda ghulam they.''"
11,"Marwan Asfar bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko dekha ke unhoney apni sawari qibla rukh bithaai aur phir uski taraf munh karkey peshab kerney lagey . maine kaha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya us se mana nahin kya gaya hai? unhoney kaha : haan ! khuli fiza mein us se roka gaya hai, magar jab tumharey aur qibley ke darmiyan koi chiz haael ho to koi harj nahin."
12,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain : main (eik baar) ghar ki chhat par chadha to dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qazaey-hajat ke liye do enton par bethey hain aur aap ka munh baitul-Maqdis ki janib hai.
13,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke ham peshab ke liye qibley ki taraf munh karen. phir maine aap ki wafat se eik saal pehley aap ko dekha ke aap qibley ki taraf munh karkey ( qazaey-hajat ke liye ( bethey they.
14,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab qazaey-hajat ka irada kartey to jab tak zameen ke qarib na ho jatey apna kapda na uthatey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Abdussalam bin Harab ne Aamash se aur unhoney Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai, magar ye sanad zaeef hai."
15,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : '' do shakhs is tarah pakhaney ke liye na niklen ke wo apni sharm-gahen kholey pakhana kar rahey hon aur baaten bhi kiye ja rahey hon, bila-shuba Allah azz-w-jall is baat par naraz hota hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko sirf Ikrima bin Ammar ne musnad bayan kya hai."
16,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain : ( eik baar ( Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peshab kar rahey they ke eik shakhs aap ke paas se guzra, usney aap ko salam kya, to aapney salam ka jawab nahin diya. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) aur doosron se riwayat ki gaee hai : '' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( farigh ho kar) tayammum kya aur phir uskey salam ka jawab diya .''"
17,"Hazrat Muhajir bin Qanfaz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzrey aur aap peshab kar rahey they. unhoney salam kya to aapney jawab na diya yahan tak ke aapney wuzu kya (aur jawab diya (aur mazrat kartey huey farmaya : ''mujhey ye baat napasand aai ke tahaarat ke baghair Allah taala ka zikr karun."" raawi ko shubha hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( عَلَى طُهْرٍ ( kaha tha ya ( عَلَى طَهَارَةٍ ( ) maani dono ka eik hi hai. ("
18,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her waqt Allah taala ka zikr kya kartey they.
19,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khala (toilet) jatey to apni anguthi utaar liya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye hadees munkar hai, (yani qabile-bharosa riwayat ke khilaf hai) jabkey maroof sanad yun hai : ibne-Juraij, Ziyad bin Saad, Zohri, Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chandi ki anguthi banwai phir usey utaar diya. . . . . mazkura baala pehli hadees mein weham Hammam ko hua hai aur usey sirf Hammam ne riwayat kya hai."
20,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do qabron ke paas se guzrey to aapney farmaya : ''unhen azab diya ja raha hai aur unhen kisi bahut badi baat mein azab nahin diya ja raha hai. raha ye shakhs ! to ye peshab se na bachta tha aur ye ( doosra ( to ye chughal khori kya karta tha.'' phir aapney khajoor ki eik taza tehni mangwai , usey do hisson mein chira aur her do qabron par eik eik ko gaad diya aur farmaya : ''umeed hai ke unke khushk honey tak unke azab mein kami rahegi . Hannad ke alfaz ( يَسْتَنْزِهُ ( '' peshab se nahin bachta tha.'' ki bajaey ( يَسْتَتِرُ ( '' parda na karta tha, hain."
21,"Janab Usman bin abi Sheba kehtey hain ke hamen Jarir ne Mansoor ke wastey se Mujahid se bayan kya hai, unhoney ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marfooan uskey ham-maani riwayat bayan ki hai. Jarir ne kaha ( كَانَ لَا يَسْتَتِرُ مِنْ بَوْلِهِ (aur abu-Muaawia ( Muhammad bin khazim (ke lafz hain : ( كَانَ لَا يَسْتَنْزِهُ مِنْ بَوْلِهِ ("
22,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Hasna (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main aur Amr bin Aas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas gaey, usi doran aap bahir nikley aur aap ke paas ( chamdey ki) eik dhaal thi , aapney usi se parda kya aur phir peshab kya. ham ( mein se baaz ( ne kaha ke dekho aisey peshab kar rahey hain jaisey ke aurat ( chup chupa kar) peshab karti hai. ye baat aapney sun li , aapney farmaya : ''kya tumhen maloom nahin ke bani-Israel ke eik shakhs ka kya haal hua tha? unko agar peshab lag jata tha to wo us hissey ko kaat daltey they. us shakhs ne apni qom ko us kaam se rok diya to usey qabr mein azab diya gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Mansoor ne abu-Waeil sey, unhoney Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se is hadees mein ye lafz kahe : ( جِلْدِ أَحَدِهِمْ ( '' apney chamdey ko kaat detey .'' jabke Aasim ne abu-Waeil sey, unhoney Abu-Musa sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye lafz kahe : ( جَسَدِ أَحَدِهِمْ ( '' apney jism ko kaat detey.''"
23,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik qom ke kodey ke eik dher par aaye aur khadey ho kar peshab kya. phir aapney pani mangwaya aur) wuzu kya, us wuzu mein aapney ( apney mozon par masah farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke) unke Shekh ( Musaddad ne kaha ke raawie-hadees Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke (is moqe par) mein aap se door hatney laga, to aapney mujhey bulaya yahan tak ke main (aap ke qarib aa gaya aur) aap ke peechey ediyon ke paas khada ho gaya."
24,"Hazrat Umaima bint Raqiqa (Raziallahu anha) riwayat karti hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas lakdi ka eik piyala tha, jo aap ki chaarpai ke nichey rakha hota tha. aap raat ko us mein peshab kar liya kartey they."
25,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' lanat ke do kamon se bacho .'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! lanat ke wo kon se do kaam hain? aapney farmaya : ''jo logon ke raastey mein ya unke saye mein pakhana karta hai.''"
26,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' lanat ke teen kamon se bacho . (yani (pani ke ghaat par pakhana kerney sey, aen raastey mein ya ( logon ke) saye mein .''"
27,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs ghusl khaney mein hergiz peshab na karey. ke baad mein wo wahin nahaega . Ahmed riwayat kartey hain : '' phir wo wahin wuzu kerega, kyonkey aksar waswasey usi se paida hotey hain.''"
28,"Humaid Himyari , Abdur-Rehman ke sahab zadey , kehtey hain ke main eik sahab se mila jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat se faiz yafta they jaisey ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki sohbat mein rahey they, unhoney bayan kya : '' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke hamara koi shakhs her roz kanghi karey ya apney ghusl-khaney mein peshab karey.''"
29,Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bil mein peshab kerney se mana farmaya hai. logon ne Qatada se kaha ke bil mein peshab kyon makruh w mamnoo hai? to unhoney kaha : ''kaha jata hai ke un mein jinn rehtey hain.''
30,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khala (toilet) se farigh ho kar nikaltey to kehtey : ( غُفْرَانَكَ ( ''aey Allah ! main teri bakhshish chahta hun.''
31,Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi peshab kerney bethey to apney zakar (khas ang) ko apney daain haath se na chhuey. aur jab koi pakhaney ke liye aaye to daain haath se istinja na karey aur jab kuch piye to eik saans mein na piye.''
32,Hazrat Hafsa zauja Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bayan karti hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna daayan haath khaney peeney aur pehanney ( jaisey kamon ( mein istimal kya kartey they aur baayan haath uskey ilawa doosrey kamon mein .
33,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka dahina haath wuzu aur khaney ( jaisey kamon (ke liye ( makhsus ( tha aur baayan haath istinja aur dusri makroohat waghera mein istimal kartey they.
34,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ( eik dusri sanad se bhi) mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat karti hain.
35,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jo shakhs surma lagaey to taaq salaiyan lagaey , jisney aisa kya to behtar kya aur jisney na kya us par koi harj nahin aur jo istinja kerney mein dheley istimal karey, usey chahiye ke taaq adad ley , jisney aisa kya to behtar kya aur jisney na kya us par koi harj nahin aur jisney kuch khaya aur phir tinkey se khilal kya to chahiye ke munh ke rezon ko phenk dey aur jo kuch apni zaban se saaf karey to wo nigal ley , jisney kya khoob kya aur jisney na kya us par koi harj nahin aur jo pakhaney ko aaye to chahiye ke koi aad le-ley , agar kuch na paey to ret ki dheri hi bana ley aur uski taraf pusht kar ley , bila-shuba shetan bani-Adam ke sirinon (pushton) ke sath khelta hai, jisney aisa kya bahut acha kya aur jisney nahin kya to us par koi harj nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko abu-Aasim ne Sor se riwayat kya to raawi ka naam . . . . Husain Himyari bataya ( na ke Hibrani (aur Abdul-Malik bin Sabah ne riwayat kya to kaha Abu-Saeed al-Khair (na ke sirf abu-Saeed. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abu-Saeed al-Khair Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se they."
36,"Sheban Qatbani riwayat kartey hain ke Muslima bin Mukhlid ne ( jo ke ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se Misr mein governer they ( Hazrat Ruwefe bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko zereen Misr ki janib apna naaib muqarrar kya. Sheban kehtey hain ke ham Janab Ruwefe bin Sabit ke sath Kom-Shareek se Alqama, ya Alqama se Kom-Shareek ki janib chaley, unki murad Alqaam hai, to Hazrat Ruwefe bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein ham mein se koi apney bhai ki kamzor si sawari ley leta, is shart par ke jo kuch bhi ghanimat mein se milega, usmein se nisf Malik ke liye aur nisf hamarey liye hoga. aur phir aisa bhi hota tha ke (maal ki taqseem mein) kisi ko teer ka phal milta, kisi ko uskey par aur kisi ko uski lathi. phir unhoney bayan kya ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Ruwefe ! umeed hai tujhey merey baad lambi zindagi milegi, to tum logon ko bata dena ke jo apni dadhi ko gireh lagaey ya taant baandhey ya janwer ke gobar ya haddi se istinja karey to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us se bari hain.''"
37,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke unhoney mazkura baala hadees bayan ki jabkey wo ( Abu-Salim ( unke sath baabe-al-Yun ke qiley par morcha band they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke al-Yun ka qila ilaaqa Fistaat mein pahad par waqey tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke) guzishta hadees mein mazkur ( Sheban Qatbani wo ibn Umayya hai aur uski kunniyat abu-Huzaifa hai.
38,Saiyedna Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haddi ya mengni se istinja kerney se mana farmaya tha.
39,"Saiyedna Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Jinnon ka eik wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unhoney kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! apni ummat ko mana farma dijiye ke wo haddi ya gobar ya koiley se istinja karen, kyonkey Allah azz-w-jall ne un mein hamara rizq rakha hai. chunanche Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se rok diya."
40,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi pakhaney ke liye janey lagey to apney sath teen dheley ley jaya karey, un se istinja kar liya karey. be-shak ye uskey liye kifaayat karengey .''"
41,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se istinja ke baarey mein puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : '' teen dhelon se ( istinja karey ( , un mein gobar na ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abu-Usama aur ibne-Numair ne bhi Hisham bin Urwa se aisey hi riwayat kya hai."
42,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke) eik baar ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne peshab kya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) pani ka lota liye aap ke peechey khadey ho gaey .) faraghat ke baad) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha umr ! ye kya hai? unhoney kaha : ye pani hai ke aap us se wuzu farma lein. aapney farmaya : ''mujhey ye hukm nahin hai ke jab bhi peshab karun ( to sath ( wuzu bhi karun. agar maine aisey kya to ( ummat ke liye ( sunnat bin jaeygi .''
43,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik baagh mein dakhil huye, eik ghulam aap ke sath tha, uskey paas lota tha aur wo ham mein se chhoti umr ka tha to usney us bartan ko beri ke paas rakh diya aap jab hajat se farigh huey to hamarey paas tashrif ley aaye aur (us moqe par) aapney pani se istinja kya tha."
44,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke ye aayat kareema ( فِيهِ رِجَالٌ يُحِبُّونَ أَنْ يَتَطَهَّرُوا ( '' us mein aisey log hain jo paak rehney ko pasand kartey hain.'' ehle-Quba ke baarey mein nazil hui thi. Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke wo log pani se istinja kartey they to unke baarey mein ye aayat utri.
45,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khala ( rafae-hajat (ke liye jatey to main aap ke liye piyaley ya chhaagal mein pani ley aata aur aap us se istinja kar letey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Wakee ki hadees mein hai, phir apna haath zameen par ragadte , phir main aap ke paas (pani ka eik (aur bartan lata to aap us se wuzu kartey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Aswad bin Aamir ki riwayat ( Wakee ki riwayat ke muqabley mein) ziyada kamil hai."
46,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf nisbat kartey huey bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''agar ahle-eman ke liye mashaqqat na hoti to main unhen Namaz Isha ko takheer se padhney aur her Namaz ke waqt miswak kerney ka hukm deta.''
47,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap farmatey they : ''agar meri ummat ke liye mashaqqat na hoti to main unhen her Namaz ke waqt miswak ka hukm deta. abu-Salma kehtey hain chunanche maine dekha ke Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) masjid mein bethey hotey they aur miswak unke kaan par rakhi hoti thi , jaisey kisi munshi ka qalam uskey kaan par hota hai, to jab Namaz ke liye uthtey miswak kar letey."
48,"Muhammad bin Yahya kehtey hain ke maine Abdullah bin Abdullah se kaha ke) tumharey walid ( Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) wuzu se hon ya be wuzu , wo her Namaz ke liye ( pabandi sey) wuzu kartey hain, uski kya wajeh hai? to unhoney jawab diya ke mujhey Asma bint Zaid bin Khattab ne bataya ke Abdullah bin Hanzala bin abi Aamir ne usey bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko) pehley pehal ( hukm diya gaya tha ke her Namaz ke liye wuzu kya karen, chahey pehley wuzu se hon ya be wuzu . magar jab unhen mashaqqat hui , to hukm diya gaya ke her Namaz ke liye miswak kya karen. chunanche ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) samajhtey they ke un mein himmat hai lihaza wo her Namaz ke liye naya wuzu kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Ibrahim bin Saad ne Muhammad bin Is-haq se riwayat kartey huey ( Abdullah ki bajaey ( Ubaidullah bin Abdullah kaha hai."
49,"Janab abu-Barda (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah ke paas aap se sawari talab kerney aaye to maine dekha ke aap apni zaban par miswak kar rahey they. ye Musaddad ki riwayat ke alfaz hain. aur Suleman ki riwayat mein ye alfaz hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya, aap miswak kar rahey they aur aapney apni miswak zaban ke kinarey par rakhi hui thi aur aap sey, aah-aah ki aawaz nikal rahi thi jaisey ke ubkai aa rahi ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Musaddad ne kaha ke hadees lambi thi magar maine usey mukhtasar kar diya hai."
50,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) miswak kar rahey they aur aap ke paas do shakhs they. un mein se eik bada (aur doosra chhota ( tha. ( usi beech mein) aap par miswak ki fazilat ke baarey mein wahi ki gaee aur ye ke aap ye ( miswak ( badey ko dey dijiye .
51,maine ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab apney ghar mein dakhil hotey to kis chiz se ibtida farmatey? farmaya : miswak se.
52,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) miswak kar rahey hotey they aur mujhey inayat farmatey ke main usey dho dun, magar main pehley usey apney munh mein pherti phir usey dho kar aap ko wapis dey deti ."
53,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' das baaten fitrat mein se hain. (yani sabiqa anbiya ki mutawatir sunnat hain aur wo ye hain : ( munchhein katrana , dadhi chhodna , miswak karna , naak mein pani chadhana (aur saaf karna ( , nakhun kaatna , (hathon , pairon aur deegar ( jodon ka dhona , baghlon ke baal ukhedna , zere-naf ke baal mundna aur istinja karna.'' yani pani se. Zakariya ki sanad mein Musab ne kaha ke main daswin baat bhool gaya hun, shayad ye kulli karna ho."
54,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye chizen fitri umur (baton) mein shamil hain yani kulli karna aur naak mein pani chadhana.'' aur mazkura baala hadees ki tarah zikr kya, magar us mein dadhi chhodney ka zikr nahin, balke khatney ka zikr mazeed hai. aur unki riwayat mein) انتضاح (ka lafz bayan kya gaya hai, ( انْتِقَاصَ الْمَاءِ (ka lafz nahin kaha gaya. ( انتضاح (ke maani hain wuzu ke baad sharm-gah ke maqam par chheentey maarna aur) انتقاص (ke maani pani ke sath istinja karna hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se bhi usi tarah riwayat ki gaee hai. unhoney kaha ke paanch umur (fitrat) sar se mutalliq hain. unhoney mang nikalney ka zikr kya aur dadhi chhodney ka nahin kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hammad ki mazkura baala riwayat ki tarah Talaq bin Habib, Mujahid aur Bakr bin Abdullah Muzni se unke moquf aqwal marwi (bayan) hain. unhoney bhi dadhi badhaney ka zikr nahin kya. aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees , jo wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain us mein dadhi badhaney ka zikr aaya hai. aur Ibrahim Nakhai se usi tarah marwi (bayan) hai aur us mein dadhi badhaney aur khatney ka zikr hai."
55,Saiyedna Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey to miswak se apna munh saaf kya kartey they.
56,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : (raat ko) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye miswak aur wuzu ka pani tayyar rakha jata tha, chunaanche jab aap raat ko uthtey to ( pehley ( qazaey-hajat kartey aur phir miswak kya kartey they."
57,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) din ya raat mein jab bhi so kar uthtey to wuzu se pehley miswak kya kartey they.
58,"Saiyedna Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke maine eik baar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan ( unke ghar mein) raat guzari . to jab aap bedaar huey to us jagah aaye jahan pani rakha hua tha, aapney miswak li aur miswak kerney lagey . uskey baad aapney ye aayaat tilawat farmaeyn ( Sura Aale-Imran ki aakhiri aayaat ( (إِنَّ فِي خَلْقِ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ وَاخْتِلَافِ اللَّيْلِ وَالنَّهَارِ لَآيَاتٍ لِأُولِي الْأَلْبَابِ.....) yahan tak ke ikhtitaam Sura ke qarib pahunchey balke Sura khatam hi kar di. phir aapney wuzu kya aur apni jaey-namaz par aagey aur do rakatein padhin. phir aap apney bistar par lot aaye aur so gaey aur jitna Allah ne chaha soey rahey, phir ( dobara ( jaagey aur pehley ki tarah kya aur phir apney bistar par lot aaye aur jitna Allah ne chaha soey rahey. phir (teesri baar) jaagey aur pehley ki tarah kya. her baar miswak kartey aur do rakaat padhtey. phir aapney witr padhey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko ibne-Fuzail ne Husain ke wastey se riwayat kya ke ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : '' aapney miswak ki aur wuzu kya aur is beech mein aap aayaat kareema (إِنَّ فِي خَلْقِ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ وَاخْتِلَافِ اللَّيْلِ وَالنَّهَارِ لَآيَاتٍ لِأُولِي الْأَلْبَابِ) padh rahey they yahan tak ke Sura khatam kar di."
59,"abu-Maleeh apney walid ( Hazrat Usama bin Umair Hazli (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala khayanat ke maal se koi sadqa qubul nahin farmata aur na koi Namaz wuzu ke baghair qubul karta hai.''"
60,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala kisi be wuzu insan ki Namaz qubul nahin karta yahan tak ke wo wuzu kar ley.''
61,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Namaz ki kunji wuzu hai, uski tehrim Allahu-akbar kehna aur uski tahleel Assalamualaikum kehna hai.''"
62,"abu-Ghutaif Hazli kehtey hain ke main Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas tha ke Zohar ki Azan di gaee to unhoney wuzu kya aur Namaz padhi, phir Asr ke liye Azan hui to unhoney ( dobara ( wuzu kya, maine unhen kaha : (jab aap be wuzu nahin huey to naya wuzu kerney ki kya zarurat hai?) to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''jo shakhs baa-wuzu hotey huey wuzu karey us ke liye das nekiyan likhi jati hain.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat Janab Musaddad ki hai, jo ( Muhammad bin Yahya ki riwayat sey) ziyada kamil hai."
63,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abdullah bin umr apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ( aisey (pani ke mutalliq puchha gaya jis par janwer aur darindey waarid hotey hain ( maslan taalaab mein dakhil ho jatey ya us se peetey hain, to uska kya hukm hai? ( aapney farmaya : ''jab pani do matkon ke barabar ho to napak nahin hota . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke) Muhammad ( ibne-al-Ula ki riwayat mein '' Muhammad bin Jaafar bin Zuber '' aaya hai jabke Usman bin abi Sheba aur Hasan bin Ali ki riwayat mein '' Muhammad bin Ibad bin Jaafar '' manqul hua hai aur yehi (doosra) sahih hai."
64,"Janab Ubaidullah bin Abdullah bin umr apney walid ( Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us pani ke baarey mein puchha gaya jo jangal mein hota hai, to unhoney guzishta hadees ki tarah riwayat ki."
65,Janab Ubaidullah bin Abdullah bin umr kehtey hain ke mujh se merey walid ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab pani do matkon ke barabar ho to napak nahin hota .'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hammad bin Zaid ne usey Aasim se moqoofan riwayat kya hai.
66,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya ke kya ham Bizaa ke kunwen se wuzu kar liya karen, jabke ye kunwaan aisa hai ke us mein haiz ke chheethdey , kutton ka gosht aur gandagi dal di jati hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pani paak hai, usey koi chiz napak nahin karti . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain, baaz ne raawi ka naam Abdullah bin Raafe ki bajaey Abdur-Rehman bin Raafe bayan kya hai."
67,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap ko bataya ja raha tha ke aap ke liye jo pani laya jata hai wo Bizaa ke kunwen ka hota hai, halanke us mein kutton ka gosht , haiz ke chheethdey aur insanon ki ghilazat tak dal di jati hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pani paak hai usey koi cheez napak nahin karti . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Quteba bin Saeed se suna wo kehtey they ke maine us kunwen ke muhafiz se uski gehraai ke baarey mein puchha to usney kaha : pani ziyada se ziyada naaf ke nichley hissey tak aata hai. maine kaha aur jab kam ho to ..? usney kaha ke sharm-gah se kam (yani raanon tak . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine zaati taur par khud apni chadar us kunwen par phela kar usey naapaa to uski chaudaai chhe haath thi aur maine uskey muhafiz se puchha , jisney merey liye baagh ka darwaza khola aur kunwan dikhlaya tha, ke aaya uski bina mein daure-nabawi se koi tabdeeli ki gaee hai? to usney kaha : nahin aur maine uska pani dekha to uska rang badla hua tha."
68,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi ehliya mohtarma ne lagan mein se ghusl kya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye, aap us se wuzu ya ghusl karna chahtey they, to ehliya mohtarma ne aap ko bataya ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! main janabat se thi (aur maine usi pani se ghusl kya hai) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( to kya hua ? (pani junbi nahin hota. ( paak hi rehta hai.'' ("
69,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aapney farmaya : '' koi shakhs thehrey huey pani mein hergiz peshab na karey ke phir usi se ghusl kerega.''"
70,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs khadey pani mein hergiz peshab na karey aur na janabat se us mein nahaaey.''"
71,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jab tumharey kisi ke bartan mein kutta munh maar jaey to uski pakizgi (ka tariqa ( ye hai ke usey saat baar dhoya jaey, un mein pehli baar mitti se ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Ayub aur Habib bin Shahid ne bhi Muhammad (bin Sirin ( se aisey hi zikr kya hai. (yani pehli baar mitti se dhoya jaey.)"
72,Janab Muhammad bin Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya hai. aur marfooan nahi riwayat kya (balke moqoofan bayan kya) aur us mein izafa ye hai : ''jab billi munh maar jaey to eik baar dhoya jaey.''
73,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kutta jab bartan mein munh maar jaey to usey saat baar dhoo, saatwen baar mitti se dhoo. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke abu-Saaleh , abu-Rizeen , Aaraj , Sabit ahnaf , Hammam bin Munabba aur Abu-Suddi Abdur-Rehman ne usey Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai aur mitti se maanjiye ka zikr nahin kya."
74,Hazrat ( Abdullah ( ibne-Mughaffal ( Muzni ( (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( eik baar ( kutton ko qatl kerney ka hukm diya magar uskey baad farmaya : '' logon ko unke qatl ki zarurat kya hai? aur un kutton ka qusur kya hai? '' phir aapney shikar aur bakriyon ( waghera) ki hifazat ke liye unke rakhney ki ijazat de-di aur farmaya : ''jab kutta bartan mein munh maar jaey to usey saat baar dhoo aur aathwein baar mitti se maanjo . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ne aisey hi kaha .
75,"Kabsa bint Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, ye ( Abdullah ( ibne-abi Qatada ke nikah mein thin , bayan karti hain ke) unke khusr ( Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu)) unke ghar ( aaye to usney unke liye wuzu ki khatir pani undela to eik billi aa gaee aur us ( bartan ( se pani peeney lagi . abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne billi ke liye bartan ko qadrey tedha kar diya yahan tak ke usney pani pi liya . Kabsa kehti hain ke abu-Qatada ne mujhey dekha ke main unke us amal ko herat se dekh rahi hun to unhoney kaha : aey bhatiji ! kya tumhen tajjub ho raha hai? maine kaha ke haan , to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' billi najas nahin hai, ye tum par ghoomney phirney waley janweron mein se hai.''"
76,"Dawud bin Saleh bin Dinar Tammar apni walida se riwayat kartey hain ke unki walida ki maalika ne usey (yani umme-Dawud ko) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan hareesa ( eik qism ka khana ( de-kar bheja to usney unhen Namaz padhtey paya . unhoney ( Namaz ke beech hi mein) ishara kya ke rakh dey . chunanche ( usi doran mein) eik billi aai aur us mein se kuch kha gaee , jab wo Namaz se farigh huin to unhoney wahin se khana shuru kar diya jahan se billi ne khaya tha aur bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye najas nahin hai, ye to tum par ghoomney phirney waley janweron mein se hai.'' aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke wo uskey joothe pani se wuzu kar liya kartey they."
77,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : ''main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik hi bartan se naha liya kartey they jabke ham dono junbi hotey they.''
78,Hazrat umme-Subaiya Johniya ( Khaula binte-Qais ( (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke eik bartan se wuzu kartey huey mera aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath baari baari bartan mein padta tha.
79,Saiyedna Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein mard aur aurten eik bartan se wuzu kar liya kartey they. Musaddad ki riwayat hai : '' mard aur aurten ikhattey eik hi bartan se wuzu kar liya kartey they.''
80,Saiyedna Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein ham ( mard (aur aurten eik hi bartan se wuzu kar liya kartey they aur usi ( eik hi bartan ( mein apney haath daltey they.
81,Humaid Himyari kehtey hain ke main eik aisey shakhs se mila jo chaar saal tak Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat mein raha jaisa ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki sohbat mein rahey they. unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai : '' aurat mard ke ya mard aurat ke bachey huey pani se ghusl karey. Musaddad ne ye izafa bayan kya hai : '' chahiye ke dono ikhattey hi ( baari baari ( chalo lein .''
82,"Hakam bin Amr , aur ye Aqraa hain, se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya hai ke mard , aurat ke bachey huey pani se wuzu karey."
83,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke eik shakhs ne Allah ke Rasool se sawal kya ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham samandar mein safar kartey hain aur apney sath ( peeney ke liye ( thoda sa pani ley jatey hain. agar ham us se wuzu kerney lagen , to piyasey reh jaeyn, to kya ham samandar ke pani se wuzu kar liya keren? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' samandar ka pani paak aur uska murda halal hai.''"
84,"Saiyedna Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se jinnon wali raat puchha ke tumharey bartan mein kya hai? unhoney kaha : nabeez (yani khajoor ka sharbat) hai. to aapney farmaya : ''khajoor pakizah phal hai aur pani paak hai. Suleman bin Dawud ki riwayat mein hai ke shareek ko weham hua aur unhoney Abu-Zaid ya Zaid kaha. (jabkey Hannaad ko weham nahin huwa, usney Abu-Zaid hi kaha.) aisey hi Hannaad ki riwayat mein) لَيْلَةُ الْجِن (ka zikr nahin hai. (aur Suleman ki riwayat mein mojud hai. ("
85,Alqama kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki) jinnon se mulaqat wali raat aap logon mein se kon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha? to unhoney kaha ke ham mein se koi bhi aap ke sath na tha.
86,Janab Ata bin abi Ribah (Rahimahullah) se manqul hai ke unhoney doodh aur nabeez se wuzu ko makruh kaha hai. aur farmaya ke mujhey un se wuzu kerney ki bajaey tayammum karna ziyada pasand hai.
87,"Abu-Khalda kehtey hain ke maine Janab abul-Aaliya ( Taabai ( se puchha ke eik shakhs jisey janabat laahiq hui ho, uskey paas pani na ho magar nabeez ( khajoor ya kishmish ka pani ( mojud ho to kya wo us se ghusl kar ley ? unhoney farmaya : nahin."
88,"Saiyedna Abdullah bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo hajj ya Umerey ke liye nikley . un ke sath mein kuch log bhi they aur wo unke Imam they. eik din namaze-Fajr ki iqaamat hui to unhoney kaha ke tum mein se koi aagey ho. (aur Namaz padhaaey (aur khud qazaey-hajat ke liye chal diye aur kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai aap farmatey they : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko baitul-khala (toilet) janey ki hajat ho aur Namaz bhi khadi ho rahi ho to chahiye ke wo pehley qazaey-hajat ke liye jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Wuhaib bin Khalid , Shuaib bin Is-haq aur abu-Zamra ne ye hadees (Abdullah-bin-Arqam aur Hisham-bin-Urwa) ki sanad se riwayat ki hai (yani us mein '' an رجل '' ka izafa hai) magar Hisham ke aksar shagrid usi tarah riwayat kartey hain jaisey ke Zuhair ne ( an (an) رجل ke wastey ke baghair ( riwayat kya hai."
89,"Janab Abdullah bin Muhammad bin abi Bakr ( Qasim bin Muhammad bin abi Bakr Siddeeq ke bhai ( se riwayat hai ke ham Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan they ke is beech mein unka khana aa gaya , to Janab Qasim khadey ho kar Namaz padhney lagey . Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye kehtey huey suna hai : ''jab khana hazir ho to Namaz na padhi jaey neez aisi haalat mein bhi ke aadmi peshab-pakhaney ko rok raha ho.''"
90,Saiyedna Soban (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen kaam kisi ko munasib nahin hain. yani : (1) koi shakhs kisi qom ki imaamat kiraaey to ahle-jamaat ko chhod kar khas apney liye dua na karey. agar aisa kya to un se khayanat ki . (2) ijazat milney se pehley hi kisi ke ghar ke andar na jhaankey . agar aisa kya to goya ( baghair ijazat ( andar dakhil hua . (3) koi shakhs peshab pakhana rokey huey Namaz na padhey yahan tak ke faraaghat hasil kar ley.''
91,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat par emaan rakhta hai uskey liye halal nahin ke peshab pakhana rokey huey Namaz padhey , yahan tak ke farigh ho jaey.'' phir Janab Saur ne mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kya. aur kaha ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ( ''jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat par emaan rakhta hai usey halal nahin ke baghair ijazat ke kisi qom ki imaamat kiraaey aur na ahle-jamaat ko chhod kar khas apney hi liye dua karey. agar aisa karey to un se khayanat ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye sanad ahle-Sham ki sanadon mein se hai, us mein unka koi shareek nahin. (siwaye Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) key.)"
92,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik saa pani se ghusl aur eik mud se wuzu kar liya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Janab Aban ne Qatada se riwayat kya to ( an (an) Safiya ki bajaey ( سمعت Safiya kaha hai. (yani maine Hazrat Safiya se suna .)
93,"Saiyedna Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik saa pani se ghusl aur eik mud se wuzu kar liya kartey they."
94,Sayeda Umme-Umaara (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu karna chaha to aap ke liye bartan laya gaya. us main eik mud ke do tihai jitna pani tha.
95,Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey bartan se wuzu kya kartey they jis mein do ratl pani aata tha aur aap eik saa (pani) se ghusl farma liya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne ( Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kerney waley shagirdon ke naam aur asnaad mein ikhtilaf ka zikr kartey huey ( kaha ke Shoba ne kaha : ( حَدَّثَنِي عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ جَبْرٍ سَمِعْتُ أَنَسًا ( magar us mein hai ke aap '' makook '' ( eik mud ( se wuzu kartey they. us mein do ratl ka zikr nahin hai. Yahya bin Adam an (an) shareek ki riwayat mein hai) عَنْ ابْنِ جَبْرِ بْنِ عَتِيكٍ ( jabkey Sufiyan ki riwayat mein) عَنْ عَبْدِاللَّهِ بْنِ عِيسَى حَدَّثَنِي جَبْرُ بْنُ عَبْدِاللَّهِ ( aaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) ko suna wo kehtey they ke saa paanch ratl hai. Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke yehi saa ibne-abi Zi'ib ka hai aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka saa usi tarah ka tha.
96,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( eik baar ( apney sahibzadey ko dua kartey suna ( jo yun keh raha tha : ( ''aey Allah ! main tujh se sawal karta hun ke jab main jannat mein dakhil hun to mujhey uski daain janib safed mehal inayat ho.'' us par Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : bete ! Allah taala se jannat ka sawal karo aur dozakh se panah maango . beshak maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''meri ummat mein kuch log aisey hongey jo tahaarat mein aur dua maangney mein had se ziyada mubaalgha karengey.''"
97,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuch logon ke dekha ke) wuzu mein jaldi ke baais unke paon khushk reh gaey aur) unki eidiyaan chamak rahi thin . to aapney farmaya : '' ( aisi ( ediyon ke liye aag ka azab hai. wuzu mukammal kya karo.''
98,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik bartan se ghusl kartey they jo peetal ka bana hua tha.
99,Janab Muhammad bin Ala ki sanad se bhi mazkura baala hadees ki manind marwi (bayan) hai.
100,Saiyedna Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke) eik baar ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye to ham ne aap ke liye peetal ke bartan mein pani pesh kya aur aapney us se wuzu kya.
101,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ka wuzu nahin uski Namaz nahin aur jo shakhs wuzu ke shuru mein Allah ka naam na ley (Bismillah na padhey ( uska wuzu nahin .''
102,Janab Rabeea (eik Taabai aur muftii Madina ( ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees : ''jo shakhs wuzu ke shuru mein Allah ka naam na ley uska wuzu nahin .'' ki sharah mein kaha hai ke is se murad wo shakhs hai jo wuzu aur ghusl karta hai aur wuzu se Namaz ki aur ghusl se tahaarat ki niyat nahin karta. ( aisey shakhs ka wuzu aur ghusl durust na hoga.)
103,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi raat ko jaagey to apna haath dhoey baghair bartan mein na duboey yahan tak ke teen baar dho ley, kyonkey wo nahin janta ke uska haath ( sotay mein) kahan kahan lagta raha hai.''"
104,Imam Musaddad se Esa bin Yunus ke wastey se bhi mazkura baala hadees marwi (bayan) hai magar us mein hai ke do baar dhoey ya teen baar. is sanad mein abu-Rizeen ka zikr nahin hai.
105,"Abu-Maryam kehtey hain, maine Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo kehtey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap farmatey they : ''jab tum mein se koi neend se jaagey to apna haath bartan mein na daley yahan tak ke usey teen baar dho ley kyonkey tum mein se kisi ko khabar nahin hoti ke uskey haath ne raat kahan guzari.'' ya farmaya : ''uska haath na maloom kahan kahan phirta raha.''"
106,"Janab Humran bin Aban , Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam , kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ko wuzu kartey huey dekha, unhoney ( pehley ( apney haathon par pani dala aur unhen teen baar dhoya , phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani dal kar jhaada , phir teen baar apna chehra dhoya , phir apna daayan haath kohni tak teen baar , phir baayan usi tarah , phir apney sar ka masah kya, phir apna daayan paon dhoya teen baar , phir baayan usi tarah . uskey baad kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha ke aapney merey is wuzu ki manind wuzu kya, phir farmaya : ''jo koi merey is wuzu ki manind wuzu karey, phir do rakaat Namaz padhey aisey ke idhar udhar ke khayalat mein mashghool na ho to Allah uskey pichhley gunah maaf kar deta hai.''"
107,"abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ne kaha ke Janab Humran kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, unhoney wuzu kya aur mazkura baala riwayat ki manind zikr kya, us mein kulli aur naak mein pani chadhaaney ka zikr nahin kya, aur) abu-Salma ne ( apni hadees mein kaha ke sar ka masah teen baar kya, phir apney dono paon teen teen baar dhoey phir ( Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney aisey hi wuzu kya aur farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney wuzu ke angon ko us se kam baar dhoey to ( bhi) kafi hai.'' aur) abu-Salma ne apni hadees mein) Namaz ka zikr nahin kya."
108,"Usman bin Abdur-Rehman Taimi kehtey hain ke ibne-abi Mulaika se wuzu ke baarey mein sawal kya gaya to unhoney kaha : maine Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, un se wuzu ke baarey mein puchha gaya to unhoney pani mangwaya , chunanche eik bartan laya gaya. unhoney usey apney daain haath par jhukaya , phir apna daayan haath pani mein dala aur teen baar kulli ki, teen baar naak mein pani dal kar jhaada , teen baar apna chehra dhoya , phir apna daayan haath dhoya teen baar aur baayan haath teen baar , phir apna haath ( bartan mein) dala aur pani liya aur sar aur dono kanon ka masah kya, unke andar aur bahir se eik baar , phir apney paon dhoey aur farmaya : kahan hain wuzu ke baarey mein sawal kerney waley? maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey hi wuzu kartey dekha tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki tamam sahih riwayaat dalalat karti hain ke unhoney sar ka masah eik hi baar kya tha. sab raawi wuzu ko teen teen baar zikr kartey hain magar (masah ke baarey mein itna hi ( kehtey ke '' unhoney apney sar ka masah kya. '' aur us mein adad ka zikr nahin kartey jaisey ke baqi aaza mein kartey hain."
109,"Janab abu-Alqama se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani mangwaya aur wuzu kya. (pehley unhoney) apney daain haath se baeyn haath par pani dala aur apney dono haathon ko pahunchun tak dhoya. Alqama ne kaha : phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya teen baar. aur purey wuzu mein teen-teen baar aaza ke dhoney ko bayan kya aur kaha ke phir apney sar ka masah kya, baad Azan paon dhoey aur kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha, unhoney aisey hi wuzu kya tha jaisey ke tum ne mujhey wuzu kartey dekha hai. phir Zohri ki hadees ki manind bayan kya balke us se bhi kamil bayan kya. (yani jis mein khushu, khuzoo se Namaz padhney aur us par ajr ka zikr aaya hai. sabiqa hadees : 106)."
110,"Shaqiq bin Salma kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, unhoney apni kalaaiyaan teen teen baar dhoein , aur apney sar ka masah ( bhi) teen baar kya. phir farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha aapney aisey hi kya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain us riwayat ko Wakee ne Israel se riwayat kya to us mein sirf itna kaha ke '' wuzu kya teen teen baar .''"
111,"Abd Khair kehtey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey yahan tashrif laye aur wo Namaz padh chukey they, unhoney wuzu ke liye pani mangwaya, to ham ne kaha ke wo pani ka kya karengey, halanke Namaz padh chukey hain, ye shayad hamen sikhana chahtey hain. chunanche eik bartan mein pani laya gaya aur sath eik tasla (khula bartan) bhi tha. unhoney bartan se apney daain haath par pani dala aur haathon ko teen baar dhoya, phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani dal kar jhaada teen baar, aapney usi chullu se kulli ki aur naak jhaadi, jis mein ke pani liya tha, phir apna chehra dhoya teen baar aur daayan bazu teen baar, phir baayan bazu teen baar, phir apna haath bartan mein dala aur apney sar ka masah kya eik baar. phir apna daayan paon dhoya teen baar, phir baayan teen baar, phir farmaya : jis ko pasand aata hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu maloom karey to wo yehi hai."
112,"Abd Khair kehtey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Fajr ki Namaz padhaai aur phir Rehba mein aagey ( koofa ke markazi mohalley ka naam tha) aur pani mangwaya. eik ghulam bartan laya us mein pani tha aur uskey sath tasla bhi tha, chunanche aapney bartan ko apney daain haath se pakda aur apney baaein hath par undela aur apney dono haathon ko teen baar dhoya , phir apna haath bartan mein dala (pani liya (aur teen baar kulli ki aur teen baar naak mein pani dala , aur phir ( Zaayda bin Qudama ne sabiqa ( hadees abu-Awaana ke qarib qarib bayan ki, phir apney sar ka masah kya, uskey agley aur pichley hissey ka aur misl saabiq hadees bayan ki ."
113,"Abd Khair kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke eik kursi laee gaee , aap us par bethey , phir pani ka eik kooza ( bartan ( laya gaya. aapney apna haath teen baar dhoya , phir kulli ki sath hi naak mein pani bhi chadhaya . dono eik chullu ke sath . aur hadees bayan ki ."
114,"Janab Zar-bin Habish se riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna, un se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke wuzu ke baarey mein sawal kya gaya tha. to raawi ne hadees bayan ki aur us mein zikr kya ke unhoney apney sar ka masah kya magar pani ke qatrey na girey aur apney dono paon teen teen baar dhoey, phir farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu aisey hi tha."
115,"Abdur-Rehman bin abi-Laila kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, unhoney wuzu kya to apna chehra dhoya teen baar , aur apni kalaaiyaan dhoein teen baar aur sar ka masah kya eik baar, phir farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey hi wuzu kya tha."
116,Abu-Haiya kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney wuzu kya aur Abu-Haiya ne bataya ke unhoney sara wuzu teen teen baar kya. aur kaha : phir apney sar ka masah kya. uskey baad apney dono paon dhoey takhnon tak. phir farmaya : maine chaha ke tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu dikhla dun.
117,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ali yani Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) merey yahan tashrif laye, aap istinja kar chukey they, aapney wuzu ke liye pani mangwaya , ham eik chhotey bartan mein pani laye aur aap ke samney rakh diya to aapney farmaya : aey ibne-Abbas ! kya tumhen dikhlaaun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kaisey wuzu kya kartey they? maine kaha : kyon nahin ! chunanche unhoney bartan ko apney haath par tedha kya aur haath dhoya , phir apna daayan haath us mein dala aur doosrey haath par pani dala aur dono haath dhoey , phir kulli ki aur naak jhaadi , phir apney dono haath ikhattey hi bartan mein daley aur dono haathon se eik lap pani liya aur apney chehrey par dala , phir apney dono anguthon ko kanon mein dala yani jo hissey chehrey ki janib tha, ( usey bhi dhoya ( phir dusri baar , phir teesri baar aisey hi kya. phir daain haath se eik chullu pani liya aur usey peshani par dala aur usey apney chehrey par bahney diya, phir apni dono kalaaiyaan kohniyon tak dhoein teen teen baar , phir apney sar ka masah kya aur kanon ke bahir ka ( bhi) phir apney dono haath bartan mein daley aur pani ki eik lap lekar apney paon par dali aur us mein) chappal ka sa ( joota tha, apney paon ko us pani ke sath mila , phir doosrey paon ko bhi aisey hi kya. ( Abdullah Kholani ( kehtey hain maine kaha : jooton samet ? ! ( ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne ( kaha : jooton samet ! maine phir kaha : jootey pehney pehney ? kaha ke joota pehney pehney hi . maine phir kaha : jooton samet ? kaha ke) haan ( jooton samet . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ibne-Juraij ki Sheba (bin Nasaah ( se riwayat Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ke mushabeh hai. us riwayat mein Hajjaj bin Muhammad ne ibne-Juraij se naqal kya hai : '' aur apney sar ka eik baar masah kya. '' aur ibne-Wahab ne yehi riwayat ibne-Juraij se naqal ki to kaha : '' sar ka masah teen baar kya. ''"
118,"Amr bin Yahya Mazni apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke unke walid ( Yahya Mazni ( ne Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, aur ye Amr bin Yahya ke dada hain, kya aap mujhey dikha saktey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wuzu kaisey kya kartey they? Abdullah bin Zaid ne kaha : haan ! chunanche unhoney wuzu ka pani mangwaya aur apney dono haathon par dala aur haath dhoey , phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani dal kar jhaada teen baar , phir chehra dhoya teen baar , phir dono haath dhoey kohniyon tak do do baar . phir dono haathon se sar ka masah kya aur unhen aagey laye aur peechey ley gaey, sar ke agley hissey se shuru kya aur guddi tak ley gaey, phir unhen wapis laye aur wahan tak ley aaye jahan se shuru kya tha, phir apney dono paon dhoey ."
119,"Janab Musaddad ki sanad se bhi mazkura baala hadees marwi (bayan) hai ke kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya , eik hi chalo sey, aisa teen baar kya, phir raawi ne mazkura baala hadees ke mutabiq riwayat bayan ki ."
120,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim Mazni (Raziallahu anhu) zikr kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aur aap ka wuzu bayan kya aur kaha : aapney sar ka masah haathon ke bachey huey pani ke ilawa ( naey pani ( se kya aur apney paon dhoey yahan tak ke unhen khoob saaf kya.
121,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadi Karb Kandi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas wuzu ka pani laya gaya , aapney wuzu kya. apni dono hatheliyan dhoein teen baar , phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani chadhaya teen baar, chehra dhoya teen baar, kalaaiyaan dhoein teen teen baar, phir sar ka masah kya aur sath hi kanon ke bahir aur andar ka ( bhi) ."
122,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadi Karb (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aapney wuzu kya, jab sar ke masah tak pahunchey to aapney apney dono haathon ki hatheliyan sar ke agley hissey par rakhen aur unhen sar par phera yahan tak ke guddi tak ley gaey . phir apney haathon ko usi jagah wapis ley aaye , jahan se shuru kya tha. Mehmood ki riwayat mein) akhbirni hareez ( ki tasreeh hai."
123,Waleed bin Muslim ne mazkura baala sanad se riwayat kya hai aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney kanon ke bahir aur andar ki taraf masah kya. Hisham ne mazeed kaha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni ungliyan kanon ke suraakhon mein dakhil kin .
124,Saiyedna Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon ko wuzu karkey dikhlaaya jaisey ke khud unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu kartey huey dekha tha. jab aap sar ke masah ko pahunchey to aapney eik chullu liya aur baaein hath par dala aur us chullu ko sar ke darmiyan kya yahan tak ke pani ke qatrey girey ya girney ke qarib they phir sar ke agley hissey se aakhir tak aur aakhir se agley hissey tak ka masah kya.
125,Janab Mehmood bin Khalid ne Waleed se mazkura baala sanad ke sath ye kaha hai ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne wuzu kya ( to wuzu ke aaza) teen teen baar ( dhoey (aur apney paon dhoey baghair shumar kiye.
126,"Hazrat Rabeea binte-Muawwiz ibne-Afraa (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laya kartey they, unka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( eik baar ( farmaya : ''merey liye pani undel kar lao .'' to unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu karna bayan kya. us mein kehti hain ke aapney apney haath dhoey teen baar , chehra dhoya teen baar , kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala eik baar aur apney dono haath dhoey teen teen baar aur sar ka masah kya do baar . sar ke aakhir se shuru kya, phir agley hissey ki janib se masah kya aur dono kanon ka masah kya, unke bahir se bhi aur andar se bhi . aur apney dono paon dhoey teen teen baar . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat Musaddad ki riwayat ke ham-maani hai."
127,"Janab Is-haq bin-Ismail ke wastey se ye bhi riwayat marwi (bayan) hai lekin us mein mazkura baala riwayat Bishr (bin Mufazzal (ke baaz Maani mein farq hai. us mein kaha hai : '' kulli ki aur naak jhaadi , teen baar .''"
128,"Hazrat Rabeea binte-Muawwiz ibne-Afraa (Raziallahu anhu) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke yahan wuzu kya to purey sar ka masah kya, ooper se sar ka masah shuru kartey they, her janib se baalon ki laton ke rukh par haath phertey they. aur aap baalon ko unki haiyat se harkat na detey they."
129,"Hazrat Rabeea binte-Muawwiz ibne-Afraa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu kartey dekha . wo kehti hain ke aapney apney sar ka masah kya, agley hissey ka , pichley hissey ka , kanpatiyon ka aur dono kanon ka eik baar ."
130,"Hazrat Rabeea ( binte-Muawwiz ( (Raziallahu anha) se marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sar ka masah kya, aur usi pani se kya jo unke haathon mein (pehley sey) bacha hua tha."
131,Hazrat Rabeea binte-Muawwiz (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu kya to apni dono ungliyan apney kanon ke suraakhon mein dakhil kin .
132,"Janab Talha bin Musrif apney walid se wo unke dada se bayan kartey hain, kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap sar ka masah eik baar kartey they yahan tak ke) haath ( '' قذال '' tak ley jatey they.'' قذال '' guddi ke shuru ko kehtey hain. Janab Musaddad ( apni riwayat mein) kehtey hain ke aapney sar ka masah kya ( sar ke) shuru se lekar aakhir tak , yahan tak ke apney haath kanon ke nichey se nikaley . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Musaddad ne kaha : maine ye riwayat Yahya (bin Saeed al-Qattan) ko bayan ki to unhoney usko munkir kaha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Imam Ahmed ko suna, wo kehtey they ke ibne-Uena is hadees ka inkar kartey they. wo kehtey they ke '' طلحة an (an) Abeeh an (an) جده ''ye kya aur kaisi sanad hai? (yani zaeef hai. ("
133,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu kartey dekha, aur sari hadees mein) wuzu ke angon ko dhoney ka ( teen teen baar zikr kya. ( magar sar ke baarey mein kaha : ( '' aur apney sar aur kanon ka masah eik baar kya. ''"
134,Saiyedna abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke wuzu ka zikr kya farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni aakhon ke koyon ( wo gosha jo naak ki taraf ho (ka masah bhi kya kartey they. aur farmaya : '' dono kaan sar ka hissa hain. Suleman bin Harab ne kaha ke ye baat abu-Umama zikr kartey they. Quteba kehtey hain ke Hammad ne kaha : mujhey nahin maloom ke aaya ye qol : '' kaan sar ka hissa hain.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farman hai ya abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ka qol . Quteba ne apni riwayat mein) an (an) Sanan abi Rabeea ( kaha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : Sanan hi ibn Rabeea hai aur uski kunniyat bhi Abu-Rabeea hi hai.
135,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid ( Shuaib ( sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wuzu kaisey kya jata hai? to aapney bartan mein pani mangwaya , phir apney haath dhoey teen baar , phir chehra teen baar , phir dono kalaaiyaan dhoein teen baar , phir sar ka masah kya aur apni shahadat ki ungliyan apney kanon mein dalin aur anguthon se kanon ke ooper ka masah kya aur shahadat ki ungliyon se unke andar ka , phir apney paon dhoey teen teen baar, phir farmaya : '' wuzu aisey hota hai aur jo koi is se ziyada karey ya kam karey to usney bura kya aur zulm kya.'' ya yun farmaya : '' zulm kya aur bura kya. ''"
136,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke) eik baar ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu kya to do do baar kya. (yani wuzu ke angon ko do do baar dhoya .)
137,"Janab Ata bin Yasar ne bayan kya ke ham se Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : kya tum pasand kartey ho ke main tumhen dikhlaaun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kaisey wuzu kya kartey they? chunanche aapney bartan mangwaya , us mein pani tha. to aapney apney daain haath se chullu liya aur kulli ki aur naak mein pani liya . phir doosra ( chalo ( liya aur apney dono haathon ko jama kar liya aur apna chehra dhoya . phir aur chullu liya aur apna daayan bazu dhoya , phir aur chullu liya aur apna baayan bazu dhoya . phir eik mutthi mein pani liya aur apney haath ko jhaada aur us se sar aur kanon ka masah kya. phir mutthi mein aur pani liya aur usey apney daain paon par chhidka jabkey us mein joota bhi tha, aur apney dono haathon se usey mila , (is tarah goya ke unko dhoya ( eik haath paon ke ooper se aur eik haath jootey ke nichey se aur phir baain paon ke sath bhi aisey hi kya."
138,Janab Ata bin Yasar se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : kya main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu na bataun? chunanche unhoney wuzu ke angon ko eik eik baar dhoya .
139,"Janab Talha apney walid sey, wo unke dada se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa, jabke aap wuzu farma rahey they aur pani aap ke chehrey aur dadhi se seeney par gir raha tha. maine aap ko dekha ke aap kulli kerney aur naak mein pani leney mein farq kartey they. (yani kulli ke liye alehda aur naak ke liye alehda pani letey they. ("
140,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi wuzu karey to apni naak mein pani ley , phir usey jhaadey (yani saaf karey.'' ("
141,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''naak jhaado (aur saaf karo) do baar ya teen baar , khoob achi tarah .''"
142,"Hazrat Laqeet bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke qabeela bani muntafiq ka jo wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya tha, mein uska sardar tha ya eik fard . jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey to ham ne aap ko ghar mein na paya . ham ne Hazrat Aaysha ummul-momenin (Raziallahu anha) ko paya . unhoney hamarey liye '' khazeera '' bananey ka hukm diya aur wo hamarey liye bana diya gaya. phir hamarey samney eik khajuron bhara tabaq laya gaya. Quteba ne lafz '' qinaa '' nahin bola . aur qinaa aisey tabaq ko kehtey hain jis mein khajuren hun. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi tashrif ley aaye aur daryaft farmaya : ''kya tumhen kuch mila hai ya tumharey liye kuch kaha gaya hai? '' ham ne arz kya : haan aey Allah ke Rasool ! ( ham ne khazeera kha liya hai. ( is beech mein jabkey ham aap ke paas bethey they, charwahey ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki bakriyan baadey ki taraf chalaain aur uskey paas bakri ka eik bacha bhi tha jo mimiya raha tha. aapney puchha : '' arey kya janwaaya hai? '' usney kaha, eik bacha hai. aapney farmaya : '' ab hamarey liye uskey badley eik bakri zibeh kar do .'' phir ( ham sey) farmaya : ''ye na samajhna ke ham tumhari khatir usey zibeh kar rahey hain. ( Janab Laqeet kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yahan lafz 'tahsibanna' farmaya 'tahsabanna' nahi. ( darasal ( hamari so bakriyan hain, ham nahin chahtey ke us se badh jaeyn . to ye charwaahaa jab bhi kisi bakri ke bacha janne ki khabar lata hai to ham uskey badley eik bakri zibeh kar letey hain.'' Laqeet kehtey hain ke (us moqe par) maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri biwi hai aur uski zaban mein kuch hai. yani zaban daraz aur bad-go hai. aapney farmaya : ''usey Talaq dey do.'' maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! uska merey sath eik waqt guzra hai aur meri us se aulad bhi hai. aapney farmaya : '' to phir usey nasihat karo. agar us mein khair hui to samajh jaeygi. aur aisey mat maarna jaisey apni londi ko maartey ho.'' phir maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! mujhey wuzu ke baarey mein irshad farmaiye . aapney farmaya : '' wuzu khoob kamil kya karo aur ungliyon ke darmiyan khilal kya karo aur naak mein khoob pani chadhaya karo siwaey iske ke rozey se ho.''"
143,"Janab Aasim bin Laqeet bin Sabra apney walid ( Laqeet bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu)) se raawi hain, jo ke wafad bani muntafiq ke sardar they ke wo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaye aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya. us riwayat mein hai.'' ham bethey hi they ke itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zor se qadam uthatey huye, aagey ko jhuk kar chaltey huey tashrif laye . aur us riwayat mein) خَزِيْرَةٌ ( ki bajaey ( عَصِيْدَةٌ ( zikr hai."
144,Janab Muhammad bin Yahya bin Faaris ki sanad se bhi ye hadees marwi (bayan) hai. kaha ke ''jab to wuzu karey to kulli kar .''
145,Saiyedna Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab wuzu kartey to pani ka eik chullu lekar apni thodi ke nichey dakhil kartey aur us se dadhi ka khilal kartey aur farmatey : ''mujhey merey rab azz-w-jall ne aisey hi hukm diya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Waleed bin Zor un se Hajjaj bin Hajjaj aur abu-Maleeh Raqqi ne ( bhi) riwayat kya hai.
146,Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik ( jihaadi ( muhim bheji to un logon ko sardi ne aa liya . jab ye log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye to aapney unhen hukm diya ke wo apni pagdiyon aur mozon par masah kar liya karen.
147,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu kartey huey dekha . aap ke sar par eik qatri pagdi thi to aapney apney haath pagdi ke nichey kiye aur sar ke agley hissey ka masah kya aur pagdi ko na khola .
148,Hazrat Mustaurid bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap jab wuzu kartey to apney paon ki ungliyon ko apni chhanguli se maltey they.
149,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main ghazwa tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha. namaze-Fajr se pehley eik maqam par aap raastey se eik janib ko ho gaey to main bhi aap ke sath mud gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna oont bithaya aur qazaey-hajat ke liye chaley gaey . wapis aaye to maine lotey se aap ke haath par pani dala . aapney pehley apney haath aur phir chehra dhoya . phir aapney apney haath ko jubbey ki aastinon se nikalna chaha magar wo tang thin , to aapney apney haath wapis aasteen mein dal liye aur unhen jubbey ke nichey se nikala aur unhen kohniyon tak dhoya , phir aapney apney sar ka masah kya, phir apney mozon par masah kya, phir aap Sawar ho gaey aur chal diye , yahan tak ke ham ne logon ko Namaz mein paya aur wo Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ko) bator Imam ( aagey kar chukey they. unhoney Namaz padhaai jabke Namaz ka waqt ho gaya tha, ham ne paya ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman unhen namaze-Fajr ki eik rakat padha chukey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) musalmanon ke sath saf mein khadey ho gaey aur Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechey dusri rakaat padhi . Hazrat Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( Namaz mukammal honey par) salam phera to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni Namaz puri kerney ke liye khadey ho gaey .) ye dekh kar) musalman ghabra gaey aur bahut ziyada tasbih kehney lagey , kyonkey unhoney Namaz mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sabqat ki thi. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam phera to farmaya : ''tum logon ne durust kya. '' ya kaha : '' bahut achcha kya. ''"
150,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( eik baar ( wuzu kya ( to ( apney sar ke agley hissey par masah kya. sath hi ye kaha : pagdi par bhi . Janab Motamir ki riwayat mein Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mozon par , apney sar ke agley hissey aur apni pagdi par masah kya kartey they. Bakr kehtey hain ke maine ye riwayat Mughira ke bete se barahe-rast suni hai."
151,"Janab Urwa apney walid Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hum-rikaab (sawari par sath) they, merey paas pani ka bartan tha, aap qazaey-hajat ki gharz se nikley , phir hamari janib wapis aaye , to main pani lekar aap ki taraf badha , maine aap ke haathon par pani dala , aapney apney haath dhoey , phir munh dhoya , phir aapney apney bazu aastinon se nikalna chahey jabke aapney jubba pehna hua tha, wo romi jubba tha aur uski aastinein tang thin is liye aap ke bazu na nikal sakey, to aapney jubbey ke nichey se apney bazu nikaley. phir main jhuka ke aap ke mozey utaarun, to aapney farmaya : ''unhen chhodo , maine apney paon un mein daley to ye dono taahir they.'' phir aapney mozon par masah farmaya. ( Esa bin Yunus ne ( kaha ke merey walid ( Yunus bin abi Is-haq ( ne kaha ke Shaabi ne kaha : mujhey Urwa ne apney baap ( Mughira (ke mutalliq gawahi di aur uskey baap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq gawahi di. (is tauzeeh se murad hadees ki tauseeq mazeed hai. ("
152,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qafley ke sathiyon se peechey ho gaey . . . . aur mazkura baala qissa bayan kya. ... us mein hai ke phir ham logon ke paas aaye to dekha ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) unhen namaze-Fajr padha rahey hain. jab unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to peechey hatna chaha magar aapney unko ishara farmaya ke jari rahen . chunanche maine aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke peechey eik eik rakat padhi . jab unhoney salam phera to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho gaey aur faut shuda rakaat padhi aur us par koi aur izafa nahin kya.  (yani sajda saho nahin kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke hazraat abu-Saeed Khudri , ibne-Zubair aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) kaha kartey they ke jisey Namaz ki eik rakat mili ho to us par saho ke do sajdey hain."
153,"Janab abu-Abdur-Rehman Sulami riwayat kartey hain ke wo Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas hazir they aur wo Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke wuzu ke baarey mein daryaft kar rahey they. Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jab aap qazaey-hajat ke liye jatey to main aap ke liye pani ley aata aur aap wuzu kartey aur apni pagdi aur mozon par masah kartey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke abu-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat kerney wala abu-Adbullah , bani-Teim bin Murra ka maula ( azad karda ghulam ( hai."
154,"Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( eik baar ( peshab kya, phir wuzu kya aur mozon par masah kya aur kaha : merey liye masah se kya chiz maane (rukawat) hai? jabkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko masah kartey huey dekha hai. kuch logon ne kaha ke masah ka hukm Sura al-Maaida ke nuzool se pehley ka hai. to Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kya : main to Islam hi sura maayda ke nuzool ke baad laya hun."
155,"Hazrat Barida (bin Husaib ( (Raziallahu anhu) raawi hain ke Najashi ( Waliye-Habsha ( ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye siyah rang ke do saada mozey hadiya bhijwaaey to aapney unhen pehna , phir wuzu kya to un par masah kya.  Janab Musaddad ne ( Ahmed bin Shuaib ki riwayat ke bilmuqabil '' حدثنا '' ki bajaey '' an (an) '' se riwayat ki aur) ''عن دلهم بن صالح'' kaha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat ehale-Basra ke tafarrudat mein se hai."
156,Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( jab apney ( mozon par masah kya to maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap bhool rahey hain? farmaya : '' ( nahin) balke tum bhool rahey ho. mujhey merey rab ne isi baat ka hukm diya hai.''
157,Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' mozon par masah kerney ki muddat musafir ke liye teen din aur muqeem ke liye eik din aur eik raat hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Mansoor bin Motamir ne apni sanad se Ibrahim Taimi se riwayat kya hai aur us mein hai ke agar ham masah ki muddat mein izafa chahtey to aap izafa farma detey .
158,"Hazrat Ubai bin Imaara (Raziallahu anhu) , jinkey baarey mein Yahya bin Ayub ka bayan hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein dono qiblon ki taraf rukh karkey Namaz padhi hai, un se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main mozon par masah kar liya karun? farmaya : ''haan!'' unhoney kaha ( kya ( eik din? aapney farmaya : '' ( haan ( eik din .'' unhoney kaha : kya do din ( bhi ? ( farmaya : '' haan do din ( bhi .'' ( kaha : kya teen din ( bhi ? ( farmaya : '' haan ! . . . . . aur jo to chahey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is riwayat ko ibne-abi Maryam misri ne ( pasand ( Yahya bin Ayub , an (an) Abdur-Rehman bin Rizin, an (an) Muhammad bin Yazid bin abi Ziyad , an (an) Ubada bin Nasii, an (an) Ubai bin Imaara se riwayat kya hai. us mein hai ke) dino ka izafa ( saat dino tak pahuncha . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaha : ''jo teri samajh mein aaye . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kahte hain ke uski asnaad mein ikhtilaf hai aur Yahya bin Ayub qawi nahin hai. is hadees ko ibne-abi Maryam aur Yahya bin Is-haq , ( سَیْلَحِینِیُّ (aur Yahya bin Ayub se riwayat kya hai aur iski asnaad mein ikhtilaf kya gaya hai."
159,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( eik baar ( wuzu kya to apney juraabon aur jooton par masah kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi is hadees ko riwayat nahin kya kartey they kyonkey Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) se maroof riwayat ye hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mozon par masah kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi ye marwi (bayan) hai : '' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne juraabon par masah kya. '' magar ye muttasil hai na qawi . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib , ibne-Masood, Bara bin Aazib, Anas bin Malik , abu-Umama , Sehal bin Saad aur Amr bin Hurais (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne bhi juraabon par masah kya hai aur yehi baat Hazrat umr bin Khattab aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se bhi marwi (bayan) hai."
160,Hazrat Aus bin abi Aus Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu kya to apney jooton aur qadmon par masah kya. Ibad bin Musa ne ( apni riwayat mein) ye alfaz bayan kiye hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap eik qom ke kazama par aaye. yani maqame-wuzu par. magar Janab Musaddad ne ( apni riwayat mein) ميضأة aur كظامة ka zikr nahin kya. phir dono mashaaikh ( Musaddad aur Ibad bin Musa hadees ke baqi alfaz bayan kerney mein) muttafiq hain : '' aapney wuzu kya to apney jooton aur qadmon par masah kya. ''
161,Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mozon par masah kya kartey they. Muhammad bin Sabaah ke ilawa ( doosrey mashaaikh ( ne kaha ke aapney mozon ki pusht (yani paon ki ooper wali janib ( par masah kya.
162,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : agar deen raey aur qiyas par mabni hota to mozon ka nichey wala hissey ooper waley ki b-nisbat masah ka ziyada mustahiq hota, magar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap apney mozon ke ooper hi masah kya kartey they."
163,"Janab Aamash apni sanad se is hadees ko riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : main paon ke nichey waley hissey hi ko ziyada laaiq samajhta tha ke usey dhoya jaey yahan tak ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap apney mozon ke ooper ke hissey hi ka masah kartey they. is hadees ko Wakee ne Aamash se apni sanad se riwayat kya to kaha : main samajhta tha ke paon ka nichey wala hissey hi is baat ke ziyada laaiq hota hai ke unka masah kya jaey, yahan tak ke maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke ooper ki janib masah kartey they. Wakee ne kaha ke '' قدمين '' se murad '' mozey '' hain. is hadees ko Esa bin Yunus ne Aamash se waise hi riwayat kya hai jaisey Wakee ne riwayat kya hai aur usey Abul-Saudaa ne ibne-abd khair sey, unhoney apney walid se naqal kya to kaha ke maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney wuzu kya to apney qadmon ke ooper ke hissey ko dhoya aur kaha ke agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye kartey na dekha hota. (to main yehi samjhey rehta ke unka nichey wala hissey hi dhoney ke laaiq hota hai.) aur aakhir tak hadees usi tarah bayan ki."
164,"Janab Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Aamash se ye riwayat bayan ki to kaha : agar deen raey aur qiyas (guman) par mabni hota to qadmon ke talwey unke ooper waley hissey ki nisbat masah ke ziyada haq daar hotey , jabke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mozon ki pusht ( ooper waley hissey ( par masah kya hai."
165,Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine safare-tabuk mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu karwaya to aapney (us moqe par) mozon ke ooper aur nichey masah kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke Janab Saur ne ye hadees Rija se nahin suni.
166,Hazrat Sufiyan bin Hakam Saqafi ya Hakam bin Sufiyan Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab peshab kartey aur wuzu kartey to ( uskey baad sharmgaah wali jagah par) chheentey maar letey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke muhaddeseen ki jamaat ne is sanad mein raawi ka naam '' Sufiyan bin Hakam '' ko rajeh qarar diya hai. jabkey baaz ne Hakam ya ibne-Hakam zikr kya hai.
167,"Mujahid . . . . . bano Saqeef ke eik shakhs sey, wo apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke unke walid kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney peshab kya aur phir apni sharmgaah par chheentey maarey ."
168,"Mujahid Hakam ya ibne-Hakam sey, wo apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne peshab kya, phir wuzu kya aur apni sharmgaah par pani ke chheentey maarey ."
169,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hotey they aur apney kaam khud hi sar-anjaam detey they aur baari baari oont charaaya kartey they. meri baari aai to seh-pahar ko main unhen wapis laya (aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein aa hazir hua ( maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is haalat mein paya ke aap logon se khitab farma rahey they. maine aap ko suna aap keh rahey they : ''tum mein se koi wuzu karey aur achi tarah ( mukammal ( wuzu karey, phir khada ho kar do rakatein padhey , apney dil aur chehrey se Namaz hi mein magan rahey to usney apney liye jannat wajib kar li .'' maine kaha : bahut khoob ! bahut khoob ! kis qadr behtareen amal hai. to merey samney se eik shakhs bola : aey Aqba ! jo us se pehley farmaya hai wo us se bhi khoob tar hai. maine nazar uthai to wo umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) they. maine kaha aey abu-Hafs ! wo kya hai? kaha ke tumharey aaney se pehley abhi abhi ye irshad farmaya hai : ''tum mein se jo shakhs wuzu karey aur achi tarah ( mukammal masnoon ( wuzu karey aur wuzu ke baad ye kalmaat kahey : أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ وَأَشْهَدُ َأَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin. wo akela hai, uska koi saajhi nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad uskey bandey aur Rasool hain.'' to uskey liye jannat ke aathon darwazey khol diye jatey hain jis se chahey us mein dakhil ho jaey. Muawiya bin Saleh kehtey hain ke mujhey Rabeea bin Yazeed ne abu-Idrees sey, usney Aqba bin Aamir se riwayat kya."
170,abu-Aqeel ne apney chacherey bhai se unhoney Aqba bin Aamir Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala ki manind riwayat ki hai aur us mein oonton ke charaney ka zikr nahin kya aur '' achi tarah wuzu kerney '' ke moqe par kaha ke phir wo ( wuzu kerney wala ( apni nazar aasman ki taraf uthaey (aur ye dua padhey (aur Muawiya bin Saleh ki riwayat ki manind bayan kya.
171,"Janab Amr bin Aamir bijli yani Abu-Asad Muhammad bin Amr kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se wuzu ke baarey mein puchha to unhoney kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her Namaz ke liye wuzu kya kartey they, jabkey ham eik hi wuzu se kaee namazein padh liya kartey they."
172,"Janab Suleman bin Barida (Rahimahullah) apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka waley din paanchon namazein eik hi wuzu se ada farmain, aur aapney apney mozon par masah bhi kya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : maine dekha hai ke aaj aapney eik aisa kaam kya hai jo pehley na kartey they. aapney farmaya : ''maine jaan-boojh kar aisey kya hai.''"
173,"Janab Qatada bin Diaama Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke eik shakhs Rasulullah ki khidmat mein aaya, wo wuzu kar chuka tha, magar usney apney paon par nakhun bhar jagah ( khushk ( chhod di thi ( dhoi na thi ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : '' wapis jao aur achi tarah wuzu karo . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye hadees Jarir bin Hazim se maroof nahin hai. usey akeley ibne-Wahab hi ne bayan kya hai aur ye riwayat b-sanad Maaqil bin Ubaidullah jazri Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi mazkura baala ki manind marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wapis jao aur achi tarah wuzu karo.''"
174,Janab Hasan Basri ne bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Qatada ki riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kya hai.
175,"Khalid ( ibne-maadan ( eik sahabi se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs ko Namaz padhtey dekha jabkey uskey paon mein dirham barabar jagah khushk reh gaee thi , usey pani nahin pahuncha tha, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey wuzu aur Namaz ke iaade ka hukm diya."
176,Janab Ibad bin Tameem apney chacha ( Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah se shikayat ki gaee ke eik shakhs dorane-namaz mein) pet mein) kuch ( harkat ( mehsoos karta hai aur usey khayal aata hai) ke shayad hua nikli hai) to aapney farmaya : '' Namaz chhod kar na jaey yahan tak ke) hawa nikalney ki) aawaz suney ya bo mehsoos karey.''
177,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bayan farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz mein ho aur apni dubur (peeth) mein koi harkat mehsoos karey, aaya hua khaarij hui hai ya nahin aur usey shubha ho gaya ho to Namaz chhod kar na jaey yahan tak ke aawaz suney ya bo mehsoos karey.''"
178,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (eik baar) unka bosa liya aur wuzu nahin kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye hadees mursal hai (yani Ibrahim Taimi aur Hazrat Aaysha ke beech raawi ghayab hai) aur Ibrahim Taimi ne Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se kuch suna nahin hai aur Faryabi waghera ne aisey hi ( ghair mausool) bayan kya hai aur Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Ibrahim Taimi chaalis saal ke nahin huey they ke wafat pa gaey . unki kunniyat abu-Asmaa thi.
179,"ummul-momenin Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( eik baar ( apni kisi biwi ka bosa liya aur Namaz ke liye tashrif ley gaey aur wuzu nahin kya. Urwa bin Zuber kehtey hain ( ye Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke bhaanjey they ( maine kaha : ye aap hi hongi , to wo hans din. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : Zaayda aur abdul-Hameed Himani ne Suleman Aamash se aisey hi riwayat kya hai."
180,"Ibrahim bin Mukhlid ki sanad se Aamash se manqul hai, wo kehtey hain ke hamarey sathiyon ne Urwa Muzni se riwayat kya, wo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se ye hadees riwayat kartey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke Yahya bin Saeed al-Qattan ne eik shakhs se kaha : meri taraf se ye baat bayan karo ke Aamash ki Habib se ye riwayat aur isi sanad se masla istihaza wali riwayat jis mein hai ke istihaza wali aurat her Namaz ke liye wuzu karey. Yahya ne kaha, meri taraf se ye bayan karo ke ye dono hadisein na honey ke barabar (yani zaeef) hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Sufiyan Sauri se marwi (bayan) hai, kehtey hain ke hamen Habib ne jo riwayaat bayan ki hain wo sab Urwa Muzni hi se riwayat hui hain, Urwa bin Zuber se kuch bayan nahin kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hamza Zayyaat ne Habib sey, usney Urwa bin Zuber sey, unhoney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki hai aur ye sanad sahih hai."
181,"Janab Urwa bin Zuber kehtey hain ke main Marwan bin Hakam ke paas gaya , wahan ye mauzu chhid gaya ke kis kis chiz se wuzu lazim aata hai? Marwan ne kaha ke sharmgaah ko chhuney se bhi . . . . .) wuzu lazim aata hai? ( Urwa kehtey hain : maine kaha ke mujhey maloom nahin. Marwan ne kaha ke mujhey Busra bint Safwan (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya , wo kehti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''jo koi apney zakar (khas ang) ko haath lagaey usey chahiye ke wuzu karey.''"
182,"Janab Qais bin Talaq apney walid ( Talaq (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke ham Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye, to eik aadmi aaya wo b-zahir badwi ( dehati ( tha, kehney laga : aey Allah ke Nabi ! aap us shakhs ke baarey mein kya farmatey hain jisney wuzu ke baad apney zakar (khas ang) ko haath laga liya ho? to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye uskey jism ka eik tukda hi to hai ! . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us riwayat ko Hisham bin Hassaan , Sufiyan Sauri , Shoba ibne-Uena aur Jarir Raazi ne Muhammad bin Jabir sey, unhoney Qais bin Talaq se riwayat kya hai."
183,"Muhammad bin Jabir . . . . . Qais bin Talaq sey, wo apney walid se isi sanad se aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kartey hain. us mein hai ke '' dorane-namaz mein '' ( agar koi haath lagaey to farmaya ke ye uskey jism ka eik tukda hi hai. ("
184,Saiyedna Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya gaya : aaya oont ka gosht khaney se wuzu lazim aata hai? aapney farmaya : '' us se wuzu kya karo.'' sawal kya gaya ke bakri ke gosht se ? aapney farmaya : '' us se wuzu na karo.'' aur sawal hua ke kya oonton ke baadey mein Namaz padhein ? farmaya : '' oonton ke baadey mein Namaz na padha karo . beshak ye shetanon mein se hain.'' aur puchha gaya ke bakriyon ke baadey mein Namaz ( padhein ya na ? ( aapney farmaya : '' us mein Namaz padh liya karo . beshak ye Mubarak hain.''
185,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik ghulam ke paas se guzrey , wo eik bakri ki khaal utaar raha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : '' eik taraf ho jao main tumhen dikhlaaun .'' ( sikhlaaoon ke khaal kaisey utaari jati hai) chunanche aapney apna haath khaal aur gosht ke darmiyan dakhil kar diya aur usey dhansaayaa yahan tak ke baghal tak chup gaya , phir aap tashrif ley gaey aur logon ko Namaz padhaai aur wuzu nahin farmaya. Janab Amr bin Usman ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kya hai yani pani ko nahin chhua aur) Hilal bin Memun Johni ke bajaey ( Hilal bin Memun '' Ramli '' kaha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha is hadees ko abdul-Waahid bin Ziyad aur abu-Muaawia ne Hilal sey, usney Ata sey, usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursal riwayat kya, un dono ( abdul-Waahid aur abu-Muaawia ( ne abu-Saeed ka zikr nahin kya."
186,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (eik baar) baazar se guzrey, aap Madina ki ooperi taraf se tashrif laye they aur kuch doosrey log bhi aap ki paas mein daain baaeyn they. aap ka guzar bakri ke eik chhotey kaan waley murda bachey ke paas se hua . aapney usey uskey kaan se pakda aur farmaya : ''tum mein se kis ka ji chahta hai ke ye qubul kar ley . ... '' aur raawi ne hadees bayan ki ."
187,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( eik baar ( bakri ka gosht khaya aur wo dasti ( shaaney (ka gosht tha, phir Namaz padhi aur wuzu nahin kya."
188,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka mehman hua , aapney ( bakri ke) pehlu ke baarey mein farmaya to wo bhoona gaya. aapney chhuri li aur us se merey liye kaatney lagey . (us beech mein) Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur aap ko Namaz ki khabar di to aapney chhuri rakh di aur farmaya : ''usey kya hua hai, khaak aalud hon uskey haath!'' aur Namaz padhney khadey ho gaey. Anbari ne mazeed bayan kya aur kaha ke meri (Mughira ki) munchhein lambi thin to aapney miswak rakh ke ooper se kaat din ya yun kaha : '' miswak rakh kar kaatey deta hun.''"
189,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dasti ka gosht khaya aur apney haath nichey bichhi dari (ya taat) se saaf kiye, phir Namaz padhney khadey ho gaey ."
190,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dasti ka gosht daanton se noch kar khaya, phir Namaz padhi aur wuzu nahin kya."
191,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey they ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein roti aur gosht pesh kya to aapney khaya , phir pani mangwaya aur us se wuzu kya, phir Zohar ki Namaz padhi , phir baqi maanda khana mangwaya aur khaya aur Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey aur wuzu nahin kya."
192,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka aakhiri amal ye tha ke aapney aag par paki chizon ke istimal se wuzu karna chhod diya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat pehli hadees ka ikhtisaar hai.
193,"Ubaid bin Samama Muradi ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz (Raziallahu anhu) jo ke as-haabe-Rasul mein se they, hamarey yahan Misr mein tashrif laye . maine unhen wahan masjid mein hadees bayan kartey suna, keh rahey they ke mujhey yaad hai ke main eik shakhs ke ghar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath majlis mein saatwan fard tha ya chata tha ke Bilal aaye , unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Namaz ki ittilaa di to ham nikley aur eik shakhs ke paas se guzrey , uski handiya aag par rakhi thi , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se puchha : ''kya tumhari handiya tayyar ho gaee hai? '' usney kaha ji haan , merey maa baap aap par qurban ! to aapney us se gosht ki eik buti li aur khatey huey chaley gaey yahan tak ke Namaz ke liye takbire-tehrima kahi aur main aap ko dekh raha tha."
194,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo chiz aag se paki ho ( uskey istimal sey) wuzu lazim hai.''
195,"Janab abu-Sufiyaan bin Saeed bin Mughira bayan kartey hain ke wo ( apni khaala ummul-momenin ( Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aaye , pas unhoney unko sattu ka eik piyala pilaya to unhoney (yani abu-Sufiyaan ne (pani manga aur kulli ki, to Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) farmaney lagin bhaanjey ! kya wuzu nahin karogey ? be-shak Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''jis chiz ko aag ne badal diya ho us se wuzu karo.'' ya farmaya : ''jis chiz ko aag pahunchi ho.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Zohri ki riwayat mein) bhaanjey ki bajaey ( bhatijey ka lafz aaya hai."
196,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) raawi hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( eik baar ( doodh nosh farmaya , phir pani talab kya aur kulli ki aur farmaya : '' us mein chiknaai hoti hai.''"
197,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke) eik baar ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne doodh piya magar ( uskey baad) kulli ki na wuzu kya aur Namaz padh li . Zaid (bin hubaab ( kehtey hain ke Shoba ne mujhey us Shekh ( Mutee bin Rashid ( ki rehnumai ki thi (ke us se hadees hasil karun ( .
198,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein nikley . . . . . yani ghazwa zatur-riqaa mein . . . . to kisi musalman ne mushrekin mein se kisi ki biwi ko qatl kar diya, to us mushrik ne qasam khai ke main as-haabe-Muhammad mein khoon baha kar rahunga. chunanche wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qadmon ke nishaanaat ki perwi kerney laga. udhar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik manzil par padaaw kya aur farmaya : '' kon hamara pehra dega? '' to us kaam ke liye eik Muhajir aur eik Ansari uthey . aapney un se farmaya : ''tum dono us ghaati ke dahaane par khadey raho .'' jab wo dono uskey dahaane ki taraf nikley ( to unhoney tey kya ke baari baari pehra dengey ( chunanche Muhajir let gaya aur Ansari khada ho kar Namaz padhney laga (aur pehra bhi deta raha .) udhar se wo mushrik bhi aa gaya. jab usney unka sarapa dekha to samajh gaya ke ye us qom ka pehredar hai chunanche usney eik teer maara aur uskey andar tol diya. us ( Ansari ( ne wo teer ( apney jism sey) nikal diya (aur Namaz mein mashghool raha ( yahan tak ke usney teen teer maarey. phir usney rukoo aur sajda kya. udhar uska ( Muhajir ( sathi bhi jaag gaya. us ( mushrik ( ko jab mehsoos hua ke un logon ne usko jaan liya hai, to bhag nikla . Muhajir ne jab Ansari ko dekha ke wo lahu-luhaan ho raha hai to usney kaha : subhanallah! tum ne mujhey pehley teer hi par kyon na jagaa diya ? usney jawab diya : ''main eik surat padh raha tha, mera dil na chaha ke usey adhuri chhodun.''"
199,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi kaam mein mashghool ho gaey aur Namaz ( Isha ( mein bahut takheer kar di yahan tak ke ham log masjid mein so gaey, phir jaagey , phir so gaey, phir jaagey , phir so gaey, phir kahen aap tashrif laye aur farmaya : '' tumharey ilawa aur koi Namaz ka intizar nahin kar raha .''"
200,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke as-haabe-Rasul (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz Isha ka intizar kartey rehtey they yahan tak ke unke sar ( neend ke baais ( jhuk jhuk jatey they. phir wo Namaz padh letey aur) naya ( wuzu na kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Shoba ki Qatada se riwayat mein ye izafa hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein hamarey sar ( neend ke baais ( jhuk jaya kartey they. Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ibne-abi Aruba ne Qatada se doosrey alfaz se bayan kya hai.
201,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Namaz Isha ki iqaamat kahi ja chuki thi ke eik shakhs khada hua aur kehney laga aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey aap se kaam hai. chunanche wo aap se sargoshiyan kerney laga yahan tak ke qom ko ya un mein se kuch ko ungh aaney lagi . uskey baad aapney Namaz padhaai aur) Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( wuzu kerney ka zikr nahin kya.
202,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sajda kartey aur) kabhi-kabhi us mein) so jatey aur kharratey leney lagtey , phir khadey hotey aur Namaz padhney lagtey aur wuzu na kartey. maine ( eik baar ( arz kya ke aapney Namaz padh li aur wuzu nahin kya, halanke aap so gaey they, farmaya : '' wuzu us par hai jo let kar soey .'' Usman aur Hannaad ne izafa kya : '' insan jab let jata hai to uskey jod dheley ho jatey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us riwayat mein ye tukda : '' wuzu us par hai jo let kar soey.'' munkar hai. usey sirf Yazid abu-Khalid Dalani ne Qatada se riwayat kya hai. jabkey is riwayat ka ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey eik jamaat ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se naqal kya hai magar wo ye tukda bayan nahin kartey aur) Ikrima ( kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( dil ki neend sey) mehfooz they aur Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri aankhen soti hain, magar dil nahin sota .'' Shoba kehtey hain Qatada ne abul-Aaliya se chaar hadisein suni hain : 1 hadees Yunus bin Matti . 2 ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki hadees jo Namaz ke baarey mein hai. 3 aur wo hadees ke qazi teen qism ke hotey hain. 4 aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki hadees ke mujhey motamid (bharosemand) aur pasandida afrad ne hadees bayan ki, un mein se eik umr (Raziallahu anhu) hain aur un mein sab se ziyada qabile-aitimad aur pasandida merey nazdik umr (Raziallahu anhu) hi hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Yazid Dalani ki hadees Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) ke samney pesh ki to unhoney mujh ko uski ( intehai ( kamzori ke baais daant diya aur kaha ke Yazid Dalani ko kya hua ke mashaaikh Qatada ki riwayaat mein) wo kuch ( dakhil kar deta hai) jo un mein nahin hota (aur is hadees ko unhoney koi ahmiyat na di."
203,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aankhen peeth ka tasma hain, to jo so jaey wo wuzu karey.''"
204,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ham gandagi par se chal kar aatey they aur wuzu na kartey they aur na ( Namaz ke beech mein) apney baalon ya kapdon ko samettey they. (us hadees ki sanad mein) Ibrahim bin abi Muawiya ne yun kaha hai : اعمش an شقيق an مسروق an Abdullah . ۔ ۔ - - - - ( (اعمش an شقيق قال قال عبدالله) اعمش hadas an شقيق (yani Masruq ke izafa ke sath)
205,"Hazrat Ali bin Talaq (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Namaz ke doran mein jo koi phuski maarey (yani baghair aawaz ke uskey maqad (peeth) se hua khaarij ho. ( to chahiye ke wo ( Namaz chhod kar) chala jaey, wuzu karey aur Namaz dohraaey .''"
206,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey bahut ziyada mazi aati thi. maine (us sey) ghusl karna shuru kar diya yahan tak ke meri kamar ( ki khaal b-wajah pani ( phatney lagi , to maine ye masla Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney pesh kya, ya aap ko bataya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab to mazi ko dekhay to ghusl na kya kar balke sirf apni sharmgaah ko dho aur Namaz wala wuzu kar liya kar . aur jab to zor se pani nikaley (yani mani nikley ( to ghusl kar .''"
207,Hazrat Miqdad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye masla daryaft kijiye ke eik shakhs jab apni ehliya ke qarib hota hai to us se mazi nikalti hai to us par kya lazim hai) wuzu ya ghusl ( ? chunkey merey ghar mein aap ki Saahibzadi hai is liye mein aap se daryaft kerney mein hijaab mehsoos karta hun. Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us baarey mein puchha to aapney farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi aisa mehsoos karey to apni sharmgaah ko dho ley aur Namaz wala wuzu karey.''
208,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind zikr kya. kehtey hain ke chunanche Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aapney farmaya : '' chahiye ke wo apney zakar aur ghadood ko dho ley . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Sauri aur eik jamaat ne pasand ( Hisham an (an) Abeeh ( ) Urwa ( ) an (an) Miqdad an (an) Ali an (an) Nabi sallallahu alaihi wasallam ( riwayat kya hai.
209,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : usko mufazzal bin Fazaala , Sauri aur ibne-Uena ne «هشام an Abeeh an علي» ki sanad se riwayat kya hai. aur ibn Is-haq ne «عن هشام بن عروة an Abeeh an المقداد an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم» ki sanad se riwayat kya hai aur us mein khasiyatein ke dhoney ka zikr nahin kya."
210,"Hazrat Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke mujhey bahut ziyada mazi aati thi aur is bina par ghusl bhi bahut ziyada karna padta tha, lihaza maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is baarey mein puchha to aapney farmaya : ''uskey liye tumhen wuzu hi kafi hai.'' maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aur jo merey kapdey ko lag jaey ? aapney farmaya : ''jahan to mehsus karey ke kapdey ko lagi hai wahan pani ka eik chullu lekar chhidak liya kar , yehi kafi hai.''"
211,Hazrat Abdullah bin Saad Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke ghusl kis chiz se lazim aata hai? aur wo pani jo pani ke baad nikalta hai? (yani peshab ke baad uska kya hukm hai) aapney farmaya : ''ye mazi hoti hai aur her nar ki mazi nikalti hai. to us se apni sharmgaah aur ghadud ko dho liya kar aur wuzu kar liya kar jaisey ke Namaz ke liye kya jata hai.''
212,Janab Haram bin Hakim apney chacha ( Hazrat Abdullah bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu)) se raawi hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha tha ke meri biwi jab dinon ( haiz ( mein ho to ( un dino ( merey liye us se kya kuch halal hai? aapney farmaya : '' tehband se ooper oopper aur) Abdullah bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( haaiza aurat ke sath mil kar kha pi leney ke mutalliq bhi puchha . ... aur hadees bayan ki .
213,Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya ke ayyame-haiz mein mard ke liye apni biwi se kya halal hai? aapney farmaya : '' tehband se ooper oopper .) halal hai) taaham us se bachna afzal hai.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye hadees qawi nahin.
214,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne un ( Sehal bin Saad ( ko khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne awwal Islam mein is baat ki rukhsat di thi (ke inzaal na honey par ghusl na kya jaey ( kyonkey logon ke paas kapdey kam hotey they, magar uskey baad ghusl kerney ka hukm dey diya tha aur us ( pehli rukhsat ( se mana kar diya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain, raawi ki murad ( Islam ka pehla hukm ( hai ke '' pani se pani lazim aata hai.''"
215,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke wo fatwa jo log diya kartey they ke ''pani, pani se ( lazim aata ( hai, eik rukhsat thi jiski Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ibtadaaey Islam mein ijazat di thi lekin uskey baad ghusl ka hukm irshad farmaya .''"
216,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( shohar ( jab us ( biwi ( ki chaar shaakhon ke darmiyan bethey aur khatney ko khatney se mila dey to ghusl wajib ho gaya .''
217,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaaya : '' pani pani se hai.'' aur abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ( Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri se riwayat kerney waley ( yehi kartey they. (yani inzaal honey hi par ghusl ko wajib jantey they. (
218,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik baar apni ( tamam ( biwiyon ke paas aaye aur eik hi ghusl kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke (eik hi ghusl ka zikr) dusri sanadon se bhi Sabit hai. yani : Hisham bin Zaid ne Anas se aur Maamer ne Qatada Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke wastey se aur saleh bin abi al-Akhzar ne Zohri Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke wastey se aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain.
219,"Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( eik baar ( apni azwaaj ke paas aaye aur her eik ke yahan ghusl kya. abu-Raafe kehtey hain ke maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap ( aakhir mein) eik hi ghusl nahin kar letey ? aapney farmaya : ''ye ziyada pakizah , umda aur tahaarat ka baais hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ( jo ooper zikr hui ( is se ziyada sahih hai."
220,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jo koi apni ehliya ke paas aaye, phir uska khayal dobara aaney ka ho to chahiye ke un dono (baariyon) ke darmiyan wuzu kar ley.''"
221,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zikr kya ke mujhey raat ko janabat laahiq ho jati hai (yani nahaney ki zarurat padti hai) to aapney farmaya : '' wuzu karo, apni sharmgaah dho aur phir so jaya karo.''"
222,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab ghusl lazim hota aur aap sona chahtey to wuzu kar letey , Namaz wala wuzu ."
223,"Muhammad bin Sabaah Bazzaaz ne ibne-Zohri ki sanad se uskey ham-maani riwayat bayan hai aur us mein izafa hai ke : aur jab aap haalate- janabat mein hotey huey kuch khana chahtey to apney haath dho letey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ibne-Wahab ne Yunus ke wastey se usko riwayat kya to khaney ke qissey ko unka qol bana diya yani Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) mauqoofan riwayat kya hai. jabkey Saleh bin abul-Akhzar, Zohri ke waastey sey wohi bayan karta hai jo ibne-mubarak ne kaha . (yani neend aur khaney dono ka zikr kya ( magar is sanad mein shak hai ke Hazrat Aaysha se riwayat leney wala Urwa hai ya abi Salma. aur Auzaai ne Yunus se b-wastey zohri Nabi (sll) sey isi tarah riwayat kya hai jaisey ke ibne-mubarak ne ."
224,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) agar haalate-janabat mein hotey aur kuch khana chahtey ya sona chahtey to wuzu kar liya kartey they.
225,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne junbi aadmi ke liye rukhsat di hai ke jab wo kuch khana peena chahey ya sona chahey to wuzu kar liya karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ki sanad mein Yahya bin Yaamar aur Ammar bin Yasir ke beech eik aadmi ka wastey hai (yani hadees munqata hai.) aur Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib, ibne-Umar aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne kaha ke junbi jab khana chahey to wuzu karey."
226,Janab Ghuzaif bin Haris kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke irshad farmaiye ! kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusle-janabat raat ke ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey mein kar letey they ya aakhir raat mein ? unhoney jawab diya ke kabhi-kabhi ibtadaaey raat mein kartey they aur kabhi-kabhi raat ke aakhiri hissey mein. maine kaha : Allahu-akbar! hamd hai us Allah ki jisney is maamley mein wusat di. maine arz kya : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ke ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey mein witr padh letey they ya aakhir mein ? unhoney kaha : kabhi raat ki ibtida (shuruat) mein aur kabhi aakhir mein padhtey they. maine kaha : Allahu-akbar! hamd hai us Allah ki jisney is maamley mein wusat rakhi. maine kaha : ye farmaiye : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Quran majeed oonchi aawaz se padhtey they ya khamoshi se ? farmaya ke kabhi oonchi aawaz se padhtey they aur kabhi dheemi aawaz aur khamoshi se. maine kaha : Allahu-akbar ! hamd hai us Allah ki jisney us maamley mein wusat rakhi .
227,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaaya : ''jis ghar mein tasweer , kutta aur junbi mojud hon us mein farishtey dakhil nahin hotey .''"
228,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haalate-janabat mein so jaya kartey they, baghair iskey ke pani ko haath lagaeyn . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ham se Hasan bin Ali Waasti ne bayan kya wo kehtey hain ke maine Yazid bin Harun se suna, wo kehtey they ke ye hadees weham hai. yani abu-Ishaq ki hadees ."
229,"Janab Abdullah bin Salma kehtey hain ke main aur merey sath do aadmi aur they, ham Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye . eik aadmi hamari biradari ka tha aur doosra mera khayal hai, banu-Asad se tha. un dono ko Hazrat Ali ne eik janib rawana kya aur kaha ke tum dono tawana aur taqatwar ho, lihaza apney deen (ka farz ada kerney ( mein khoob himmat dikhaana. phir khadey huey aur baitul-khala (toilet) mein chaley gaey, phir nikley aur pani mangwaya , us se eik chullu liya aur us se ( apna haath munh ( dhoya aur Quran padhney lag gaey . haazirin ne us par aetraz kya to unhoney kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala (toilet) se nikaltey aur hamen Quran padhatey they. aur hamarey sath gosht khatey they aur aap ke liye koi chiz Quran padhney se maane (rukawat) na hoti thi siwaey iske ke janabat se hon."
230,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un se miley aur (musaafe ke liye ( unki taraf apna haath badhaya to unhoney kaha ke main junbi hun. aapney farmaya : ''musalman napak ( paleed ( nahin hota.''
231,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujh se Madiney ke eik raastey mein miley aur main junbi tha, lihaza mein wahan se khisak gaya aur ja kar ghusl kya, phir wapis aaya. aapney puchha : Abu-Huraira tum kahan they? maine kaha : main janabat se tha, maine munasib na jana ke tahaarat ke baghair aap ki majlis mein bethun. aapney farmaya : ''subhan Allah! musalman najas nahin hota."
232,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur) dekha ke) baaz as-haab ke gharon ke darwazey masjid ki janib khultey hain to aapney farmaya : '' un gharon (key darwazon ( ko masjid ke rukh se pher do.'' aap dobara tashrif laye aur un logon ne koi tabdeeli na ki thi, is bina par ke shayad koi rukhsat nazil ho jaey. to aap unki taraf nikley aur farmaya : ''un gharon ke rukh masjid ki janib se pher lo. be-shak main masjid ko haaiza aurat aur kisi junbi ke liye halal nahin karta. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke raawi hadees (Aflat bin khalifa ka doosra naam ( Fulait Aamiri ( bhi) hai."
233,"Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke) eik din ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki Namaz mein dakhil huye, phir apney haath se ishara kya ke apni apni jagahon par thehrey raho. phir tashrif laye to (us haal mein they ke) aap ke sar se pani ke qatrey tapak rahey they aur aapney unhen Namaz padhai."
234,"Hazrat Hammad bin Salma ne mazkura baala sanad se uskey ham-maani bayan kya. aur us riwayat ke shuru mein hai ke aapney takbir kahi aur aakhir mein hai ke jab Namaz puri ki to farmaya : ''main mehaz insan hun aur main janabat se tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke usey Zohri se abu-Salma ne , unhoney Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya to kaha : jab aap apney musalley par khadey ho gaey aur hamen intizar hua ke aap takbir kahen to aap wahan se chal diye aur farmaya : '' jaisey ho ( wesay hi thehrey raho!'') aur usey Ayub aur ibn Aun aur Hisham (teeno) ne Muhammad yani ibne-Sirin se (mursal taur par) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya hai ke aapney takbir kahi, phir apney haath se logon ki taraf ishara farmaya : ''beth jao.'' aur khud chaley gaey aur ghusl kya. aur usi tarah Malik ne Ismail bin abi Hakim se unhoney Ata bin Yasar se riwayat kya aur ye kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik Namaz mein takbir kahi. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain aur aisey hi Muslim bin Ibrahim ne hamen apni sanad se bayan kya ke ham se Aban ne bayan kya, wo Yahya se riwayat kartey hain wo Rabeea bin Muhammad se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ke aapney takbir kahi ."
235,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi gaee aur logon ne safein bana lin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye yahan tak ke jab apni jagah par khadey ho gaey to aap ko yaad aaya ke aapney ghusl nahin kya hai to logon se farmaya : '' apni apni jagah par thehrey raho .'' phir aap apney ghar gaey, phir hamarey paas wapis aaye to aap ke sar se pani ke qatrey tapak rahey they aur aapney ghusl kya tha (aur is beech mein) ham safon mein khadey rahey . ye ibne-Harb ke lafz hain jabkey Ayash ke lafz hain : ham barabar khadey rahey, aap ka intizar kartey rahey yahan tak ke aap tashrif laye aur ghusl karkey aaye ."
236,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya gaya ke insan ( apney jism ya kapdon par) nami mehsoos karta hai magar usey ehtilaam (ya khuwab) yaad nahin aata. aapney farmaya : ''ghusl karey.'' aur us aadmi ke mutalliq puchha gaya jo samajhta hai ke usey ehtilaam hua hai magar (jism ya kapdon par) koi nami nahin paata? aapney farmaya : ''us par ghusl nahin hai.'' to umme-Saleem (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke agar aurat usi tarah dekhay to kya us par ghusl hai? aapney farmaya : ''haan! aurten ( bhi) bila-shuba mardon hi ki manind hain.''
237,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat umme-Sulaim ansaariya (Raziallahu anha)... walida Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ...ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! bila-shuba Allah taala haq baat se nahin sharmata. ye farmaiye ke jab aurat khuwab mein wo kuch dekhey jo mard dekhta hai to kya wo ghusl karey ya nahin? Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chahiye ke ghusl karey jab wo pani (nikalney) ka asar mehsoos karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Zubaidi, Aqeel, Yunus aur Zohri ke bhatijey (Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Muslim, chaaron ne) Zohri sey, aur aisey hi ibne-abi al-wazir (Ibrahim bin Umar) ne Malik ke wastey, Zohri se usi tarah riwayat kya hai (yani ye mukaalma Hazrat Aaisha aur umme-Sulaim ke beech hua hai) neez Musaafe Hajabi ne (bhi) Zohri ki muwaafiqat mein Urwa ke wastey Hazrat Aaysha se yehi riwayat kya hai, magar Hisham bin Urwa Urwa ke wastey Zenab binte-abi Salma ki sanad se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke umme-Sulaim Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai thi."
238,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik bartan farq se ghusle-janabat kar liya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Maamer ne Zohri ke wastey is hadees mein riwayat kya hai ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik bartan se ghusl kar liya kartey they jis main eik farq ke barabar pani aata tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke ibne-Uena ne bhi hadees Malik ki manind riwayat kya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : maine Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna, wo keh rahey they ke, farq (eik bartan hai) us mein ba-eitibaar miqdaar sola ratl aatey hain aur maine unko suna, keh rahey they ke ibne-abi Zi'ib ka saa (ba-eitibare-wazan) ke paanch ratl aur tihai ratl ke barabar hota hai. kaha gaya ke jo log saa ko aath ratl ke barabar batatey hain? unhoney farmaya ke unka qol (sahih aur) mehfooz nahin hai. kehtey hain ke maine Imam Ahmed ko suna, wo keh rahey they ke jo shakhs hamarey us ratl ke mutabiq paanch ratl aur eik tihai ratl ( sharae eik saa) sadqa fitr ada kar dey, to usney pura fitraana ada kar diya. kaha gaya : (Madiney ki) Sehaani khajoor bhari hoti hai. kaha : Sehaani behtareen khajoor hai? kaha : main nahin janta."
239,Hazrat Jubair bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) raawi hain ke kuch logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan ghusle-janabat ka zikr kya to aapney farmaya : '' magar main to apney sar par pani ke teen lap daalta hun.'' aur sath hi aapney apney dono haathon se ishara farmaya.
240,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghusle-janabat karna hota to doodh ke dol ki tarah ka bartan talab kartey. phir apney dono haathon se pani letey aur apney sar ki daain janib se shuru kartey phir baain janib phir apney dono haathon se pani letey aur apney sar par daltey they.
241,"Janab Jume bin Umair . . . . . . aur ye bani Taimillah bin Solba ke khaanwaade se hain. . . . . . kehtey hain ke main apni walida aur khaala ke sath Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aaya tha. un dono mein se eik ne un se puchha ke ghusl mein aap log kaisey kartey they? to Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( pehley ( Namaz ke wuzu ki tarah ka wuzu kartey phir apney sar par teen baar pani daltey they, magar ham apni chotiyon ki wajeh se paanch baar daalti thin ."
242,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat kartey. ... . Suleman ki riwayat mein hai. ... . ibtida (shuruat) kartey to apney daain haath se baain par pani daltey . aur Musaddad ki riwayat mein hai apney dono haath dhotey , bartan ko apney daain haath par ondha kartey. uskey baad dono mashaaikh riwayat kerney mein muttafiq hain ke phir apni sharmgah dhotey aur baqaul Musaddad apney baaein hath par pani daltey aur kabhi-kabhi wo (Hazrat Aaisha) sharmgaah ka zikr kinaaya se kartin. ... phir aap Namaz ke wuzu ki tarah ka wuzu kartey, phir apney haath pani mein daltey aur apney baalon ka khilal kartey , jab samajhtey ke jald tar ho gaee hai ya saaf ho gaee hai to apney sar par teen lap pani daltey (aur aakhir ghusl mein) agar koi pani bach rehta to apney jism par dal letey."
243,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat ka irada kartey to apney haathon se ibtida (shuruat) kartey, unhen dhotey, phir apni sharmgaah ke girda-gird dhotey (yani sharmgah, peeth, raanein aur ghutnon ke peechey wala hissey dhotey) aur us par pani bahaatey phir jab ( sharm-gah ki safai ke baad) apney haathon ko saaf kar letey to (mazeed tahaarat ke liye) un haathon ko deewar par maartay (yani mitti se maltey) phir wuzu shuru kartey aur apney sar par pani daltey."
244,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : agar chaho to main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke deewar par haath maarney ke nishan dikha sakti hun jahan ke aap ghusle-janabat kya kartey they.
245,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye ghusl ka pani rakha . aap ghusle-janabat karna chahtey they. aapney bartan ko apney daain haath par ondha kya aur usey do ya teen baar dhoya . phir apni sharmgaah par pani dala aur baaein hath se usey dhoya . phir apna haath zameen par maara aur usey dhoya . phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala. apna chehra aur haath dhoey, phir apney sar aur jism par pani dala , phir aap eik taraf ho gaey aur apney paon dhoey . phir maine aap ko roomaal diya magar aapney nahin liya aur jism se pani jhaadney lagey .) Aamash kehtey hain ( maine ye baat Ibrahim Nakhai se zikr ki) ke ghusl ke baad jism poncha jaey ya nahin) to usney kaha : Sahaba us mein koi harj nahin samajhtey they lekin aadat bana leney ko bura jantey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Musaddad kehtey hain ke maine Abdullah bin Dawud se kaha ke Sahaba kiram ( ghusl ke baad kapdey se jism khushk kerney ko) bator aadat makruh jantey they? kaha aisey hi hai lekin maine apni kitab mein usey is tarah paya hai."
246,Janab Shoba ( abu-Adbullah bin Dinar maula ibne-Abbas ( bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) jab ghusle-janabat kartey to apney daain haath se baaeyn par saat baar pani daltey . phir apni sharmgaah dhotey. eik dafa wo bhool gaey ke kitni baar pani dala hai to mujh se poochhney lagey ke maine kitni baar pani dala hai? maine kaha mujhey maloom nahin. kaha na rahey teri maa! janney se tujhey kya baat rukawat huwi? phir wuzu kya jaisey ke Namaz ke liye hota hai. phir apney jism par pani daltey aur kehtey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usi tarah se tahaarat hasil kya kartey they.
247,Saiyedna Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke (shuroo shuru mein) namazein pachas aur ghusle-janabat saat saat baar tha. usi tarah wo kapda jisey peshab lag jata uska dhona bhi saat baar tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is baarey mein) kami ka ( sawal barabar kartey rahey yahan tak ke namazon ko paanch aur ghusle-janabat aur peshab lagey kapdey ka dhona eik baar kar diya gaya.
248,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her her baal ke nichey janabat hai, lihaza apney baalon ko dhoo aur jism ko khoob saaf karo . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Haris bin Wajeeh ki) mazkura ( hadees munkar hai. aur wo zaeef hai."
249,Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney janabat main eik baal ki jagah bhi chhod di aur usey na dhoya to uskey sath aag mein aisey aur aisey kya jaeyga.'' (yani azab diya jaeyga ( Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : main usi wajeh se apney sar ka dushman bin gaya hun. mein usi wajeh se apney sar ka dushman bin gaya hun. mein usi wajeh se apney sar ka dushman bin gaya hun. aap apney baal mundaaey rakhtey they.
250,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusl kartey, do rakatein ada kartey aur namaze-Fajr padhtey aur main nahin samajhti ke aap ghusl ke baad wuzu ki tajdeed kartey they."
251,"ummul-momenin Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke musalmanon ki eik khatoon ne puchha ..... Zuhair ki riwayat hai ke . ..khud Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! main apney sar ke baal sakht karkey baandhti hun, to kya ghusle-janabat ke moqe par unhen kholun? aapney farmaya : ''terey liye yehi kafi hai ke to apney sar par dono haath bhar kar teen baar pani dal ley. Zuhair ke alfaz hain ( تُحْثِي عَلَيْهِ ثَلَاثَ حَثَيَاتٍ مِنْ مَاءٍ ( ) aur maani eik hi hai) aur uskey baad baqi jism par pani baha liya kar. is tarah to paak ho jaeygi."
252,ummul-momenin Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke eik aurat unke paas aai aur yehi masla daryaft kya. wo kehti hain ke maine uski khatir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha . ... aur ooper ki hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya. ... us riwayat mein hai : '' her lap dalney ke baad apney baalon ki chotiyan nichod dal.''
253,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham mein se jab kisi ko ghusle-janabat ki zarurat hoti to wo is tarah yani dono hatheliyan ikhatti karkey teen lap pani liya karti aur apney sar par daalti aur (phir baqi jism par) eik chullu lekar us janib daalti aur doosra chullu dusri janib.
254,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham ghusl kya kartin aur hamarey sar par lep hota aur ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath hoti thin. ehram mein aur ghair ehram mein bhi.
255,"Janab Shureh bin Ubaid kehtey hain ke mujhey Jubair bin Nafair ne ghusle-janabat ke baarey mein fatwa diya aur kaha ke Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko bayan kya ke logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is baarey mein poochha, to aapney farmaya : ''mard ko apney baal puri tarah kholney chaahiyen aur wo unhen achi tarah dhoey yahan tak ke pani baalon ki jadon tak pahunch jaey lekin aurat ke liye baalon ko kholna lazimi nahin hai. usey sirf apney dono haathon se teen lap pani dalna kafi hai.''"
256,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq bayan karti hain ke aap apna sar khitmi se dho liya kartey they jabkey aap junbi hotey aur aap usi par kifaayat kartey mazeed pani na bahaatey .
257,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke jo pani mard w aurat ke darmiyan behta hai, uskey baarey mein unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pani ka eik chullu letey , (aur ( mujh par pani daltey (ya pani , mazi ya mani par daltey ( phir doosra chullu letey aur usko apney ooper dal letey (ya mazeed uskey ooper baha detey) ."
258,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke yahudi apni aurton ko unke haiz ke dino mein gharon se nikal detey they. unke sath ikhattey na khatey they, na peetey they aur na yakjaa rehtey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us baarey mein puchha gaya tu Allah taala ne ye irshad nazil farmaya : ( َيَسْأَلُونَكَ عَنِ الْمَحِيضِ . ... ( ''ye log aap se haiz ke baarey mein sawal kartey hain aap un se keh dijiye ke ye gandagi hai. haiz mein aurton se alehda raho.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni biwiyon se gharon ke andar ikhattey mil jal kar raho. aur tum sab kuch kar saktey ho siwaye nikah (yani jima (ke .'' ( yahudiyon ko ye maloom hua) to yahudi kehney lagey ye aadmi sab baton mein hamari mukhalifat hi karta hai. chunanche Hazrat Usaid bin Huzair aur Ibad bin Bishr (Raziallahu Anhuma) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! yahudi aisey aisey kehtey hain to kya ham un ayyame-haiz mein amale-nikah (yani haqeeqi jinsi amal) bhi na kar liya keren? is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra badal gaya. yahan tak ke hamen yaqeen tha ke aap un par naraz huey hain. phir wo dono chaley gaey aur) unke nikaltey hi) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas doodh ka hadiya aa gaya to aapney unko peechey se bulwa bheja aur unhen doodh pilaya . is tarah hamen tasalli hui ke aap ghussa nahin huey hain."
259,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main ( khana khatey huey ( haddi par se gosht nochti, aur main haiz se hoti, phir usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko deti, aap (usey qubul farma letey aur) usi jagah apna munh rakhtay, jahan se maine khaya hota aur main pani peeti phir aap ko deti, to aap apney lab wahin lagatey, jahan se maine piya hota."
260,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) batati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna sar Mubarak meri god mein rakh detey aur Quran padhney lagtey, jabkey main dinon se hoti thi."
261,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey masjid mein se chataai thama do.'' maine kaha : main haiz se hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tera haiz terey haath mein nahin hai.''
262,Hazrat Muaza ne bayan kya ke eik aurat ne Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kya ke aaya haaiza ( apney ayyame-haiz ki) namazon ki qaza dey? to unhoney kaha : kya to haruri hai? bila-shuba ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hotey huey haiz se hoti thin to ham kisi Namaz ki qaza nahin deti thin aur na hamen uska hukm hi diya jata tha.
263,"Hazrat Muaza adwiya ne Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se yehi hadees riwayat ki hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is mein ye izafa hai, hamen rozey ki qaza kerney ka hukm diya jata tha aur namazon ki qaza kerney ka hukm na diya jata tha.''"
264,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us shakhs ke baarey mein jo apni biwi se haalat haiz mein mujaamiat karta hai riwayat kya hai ke aapney farmaya : ''eik Dinar sadqa karey ya aadha deenar.'' Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke sahih riwayat aisey hi hai ke ''eik Dinar ya aadha deenar.'' lekin Shoba is riwayat ko kabhi-kabhi marfooan bayan na kartey they. (balke Hazrat ibne-Abbas par moquf kar detey they.)
265,Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka irshad hai : agar shohar apni biwi ke paas haiz ke khoon ke ibtidaai (shuruati) dino mein aaye to eik Dinar dey aur agar khoon ruk janey ke dinon mein aaye to aadha Dinar dey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ibne-Juraij ne Abdul-Karim se aur unhoney Muqsim se aisey hi riwayat kya hai.
266,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar koi aadmi apni ehliya ke paas uskey ayyame-haiz mein aaye , to chahiye ke aadha Dinar sadqa dey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Ali bin Bazima ne Muqsim sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursalan bayan kartey hain. aur Auzaai ne Yazid bin abi Malik sey, unhoney Abdul-Hameed bin Abdur-Rehman sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya : aapney usey hukm diya ke wo eik Dinar ka 2 / 5 sadqa karey. magar ye sanad maazil hai. (yani us mein do raawi yakey baad deegar saaqit hain ( ."
267,ummul-momenin Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni azwaaj mein se kisi eik ke sath let jaya kartey they jabkey wo haiz se hoti aur us par aadhi raanon tak ya ghutnon tak kapda hota aur wo us kapdey se apney (Zereen) jism ko dhaanpey hoti thi.
268,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham aurton ko hukm farmatey ke jab ham mein se koi haiz se ho to apni chadar achi tarah baandh liya karey. phir shohar (ko ijazat hai ke) uskey sath let jaey. aur) Shoba ne ( eik baar ( يضاجعها ( ki bajaey ( يباشرها (ka lafz riwayat kya.
269,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti thin ke main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik hi chadar mein raat guzaarey aur main haiz se hoti. agar aap ko mujh se kuch lag jata to itni jagah dho letey us se aagey na badhtey aur Namaz padh letey. aur agar kapdey ko kuch lag jata to bhi usi qadr jagah dhotey us se aagey na badhtey aur usi mein Namaz padh letey.
270,"Janab Umara bin Ghurab kehtey hain ke unki phuphi ne unhen bataya ke unhoney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kya, kaha ke ham mein se eik haaiza hoti hai aur uskey liye aur uskey shohar ke liye sirf eik hi bistar hota hai. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik baar ki baat batati hun ke aap ( ghar mein) tashrif laye aur apni masjid mein chaley gaey . . . . . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha us se murad ghar mein Namaz ki jagah par . . . . . phir aap farigh na huey yahan tak ke meri aankhen bojhal ho gaeen . (yani neend ne aa liya (aur aap ko sardi ne sataya to farmaya : ''merey qarib ho jao .'' maine kaha : main haiz se hun. aapney kaha : '' apni raanon se kapda hataao .'' maine apni raanon se kapda hata liya to aapney apna gaal aur seena meri raanon par rakh diya aur main bhi aap par jhuk gaee , yahan tak ke aap garm ho gaey aur so rahey ."
271,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) riwayat karti hain, farmati hain : jab mujhey haiz aata to main bistar se utar kar chatai par aa jati phir ham (beeviyan) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qarib na hoti thin yahan tak ke paak ho jatin ."
272,Janab Ikrima kisi zauja Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se raawi hain kehti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) agar apni kisi ehliya se kuch khahish kartey aur wo haiz se hoti to uski sharmgaah par kapda dal detey .
273,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey (yani beeviyon ke) shiddate-haiz ke dino mein hamen hukm detey ke ham apni chadar kas ke baandh lein aur phir hamarey sath let jatey. ... aur tum mein se kon hai jisey apney jazbaat par is qadr zabt ho jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tha?
274,"Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) zauja Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main eik aurat ko bahut khoon aata tha to uskey liye umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aapney farmaya : ''usey chahiye ke ye aariza laahiq honey se pehley , mahiney ( mein haiz (ke dino aur raaton ki ginti ka khayal karey aur istihaza waley mahiney mein usi andazey se Namaz chhod dey . jab ye din guzar jaeyn to ghusl kar ley aur kapdey ka langot baandhey rahey aur Namaz padhti rahey .''"
275,eik aadmi ne Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kya ke eik aurat ko bahut khoon aata tha. aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kya. . . . . . us riwayat mein hai ke jab ye din guzar jaeyn aur Namaz ka waqt aa jaey (yani Namaz padhney ke din aa jaeyn ( to chahiye ke ghusl karey. baqi riwayat sabiqa hadees ke ham-maani hai.
276,eik Ansari se riwayat hai ke eik khatoon ko bahut ziyada khoon aata tha. aur mazkura baala hadees Leis ke ham-maani bayan kya. kaha ke jab ye dinon guzar ley aur Namaz ka waqt aa jaey to ghusl karey. aur uskey ham-maani zikr kya.
277,Sakhr bin Juweriya Naafe se Leis ki asnaad se aur uskey ham-maani riwayat kartey hain. kaha : ''ayyame-haiz ki ginti ke mutabiq Namaz chhod dey . phir jab Namaz ka waqt ho jaey ( Namaz ke dinon aa jaeyn ( to ghusl karey aur kapdey ka langot baandhey aur Namaz padhey.''
278,"Suleman bin Yasar , Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se yehi qissa bayan kartey hain. us mein hai ke '' Namaz chhod dey aur uskey ilawa mein ghusl karey aur kapdey ka langot baandhey aur Namaz padhey.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Hammad bin Zaid ne Ayub ke wastey ye riwayat bayan ki to us mein mustihaza khatoon ka naam Fatima binte-abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) bataya ."
279,"Janab Urwa , Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kartey hain ke unhoney kaha : Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se khoon ke mutalliq puchha : Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain maine unki lagan dekhi thi ke khoon se bhari hui thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : ''is aarize se pehley ki aadat ke mutabiq Namaz se ruki raho jaisey ke ba-qaeeda tumhen haiz rokta tha, phir ghusl kar lo.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha Quteba ne eik hadees mein is riwayat ki sanad mein Jaafar ka nasab ''Jaafar bin Rabeea'' dusri martaba mein wazeh kya. (yani unhen Jaafar ke ibn Rabeea honey mein shak tha ( jabkey Ali bin Ayash aur Yunus bin Muhammad ne Leis se riwayat kya to un dono ne basaraahat ( baghair shak ke) '' Jaafar bin Rabeea ''kaha ."
280,Janab Urwa bin Zuber kehtey hain ke Fatima binte-abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) ne unhen bataya ke usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya aur khoon ki shikayat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''ye eik rag (ka khoon ( hai. tum zara ghor se dekho jab tumhara haiz aaye to Namaz chhod do aur jab haiz guzar jaey to tahaarat hasil karo aur doosrey haiz ke dinon aaney tak Namaz padhti raho.''
281,"Janab Urwa bin Zuber ne kaha ke mujh se Fatima binte-abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya, unhoney Asma se kaha tha ya Asma ne mujh se bayan kya ke un se Fatima binte-abi Habish ne kaha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se poochho . chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hukm diya ke un dinon mein bethi rahey (aur Namaz na padhey ( jin mein (us aarizey se pehley ( betha karti thi , phir ghusl karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : usko Qatada ne Urwa bin Zuber se wo Zenab bint umme-Salma se riwayat kartey hain ke Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash ko istihaza ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hukm diya ke apney haiz ke dinon mein Namaz chhod dey phir ghusl karey aur Namaz padhey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Qatada ne Urwa se kuch nahin suna hai. aur ibne-Uena ne ( zohri an (an) umra an (an) Aaisha» ki hadees mein ye izafa kya hai, kaha : Umme-Habiba ko istihaza hota tha to usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se poochha, aapney usey hukm diya ke apney haiz ke dinon mein Namaz chhodey rahey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye alfaz ibne-Uena ka weham hain. Huffaz ki hadees mein Zohri se wohi marwi (bayan) hai jo Suhel bin abi Saleh ne zikr kya. aur Humaidi ne ye hadees ibne-Uena se riwayat ki to us mein) tada' الصلاة أيام أقرائها (ke alfaz zikr nahin kiye. aur Qumair bint Amr zauja Masruq ne Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kya hai : '' istihaza wali apney haiz ke dinon ki namazein chhodey rahey, phir ghusl karey. aur Abdur-Rehman bin Qasim ne apney walid se bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey (mustahaza ko) hukm diya tha ke apney haiz ke dinon ke barabar namazein chhod dey. aur abu-Bashar Jaafar bin abi Wahshiya ne Ikrima sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko istihaza ho gaya. aur usi ke misl zikr kya.  aur Shareek ne abu-Yaqzan sey, wo Adi bin Sabit sey, wo apney walid sey, wo us (Adi) ke nana sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain : '' istihaza wali apney haiz ke dinon ki namazein chhodey rahey, phir ghusl karey aur Namaz padhey.'' aur Ala bin Musaiyab ne hukm sey, unhoney abu-Jaafar se riwayat kya kaha : Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ko istihaza ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko hukm diya : ''jab unke dinon guzar jaeyn to ghusl keren aur Namaz padhein.'' aur Saeed bin Jubair ne Hazrat Ali aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kya ke mustahaza apney ayyame-haiz mein bethi rahey. aur aisey hi Ammar maula bani Hashim aur Talaq bin Habib ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas se riwayat kya. aur aisey hi Maaqil Khas-ami ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se aur Shobi ne Qumair zauja Masruq sey, unhoney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hasan, Saeed bin musaiyab, Ata, mak-hool, Ibrahim, Salim aur Qasim ka yehi qol hai ke mustahaza apney ayyame-haiz ki namazein chhodey rahey."
282,"Janab Urwa Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se raawi hain, unhoney kaha ke Fatima binte-abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) Rasul Allah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ayen aur kaha ke main aisi aurat hun jisey istihaza hota hai aur paak nahin hoti hun, to kya Namaz chhod dun? aapney farmaya : ''ye eik rag (ka khoon hota ( hai, haiz nahin. jab haiz aaye to Namaz chhod diya karo aur jab khatam ho jaey to apney se khoon dhoo aur Namaz padho .''"
283,"Qaanabi ne Malik ke wastey se Hisham se pasand Zuhair usi ke ham-maani bayan kya, kaha : ''jab haiz aaye to Namaz chhod do . aur jab uskey b-qadr ( b-qadr aadat saabiq dinon ( guzar jaeyn to khoon ko dhoo aur Namaz padho .''"
284,"Buhaiya se riwayat hai, kaha ke maine eik aurat ko suna jo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se poochh rahi thi ke jis aurat ka nizam haiz kharab ho gaya ho aur usey bahut ziyada khoon aata ho ( to wo kya karey ? ( to ( unhoney kaha ( mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya hai ke main usey kahun ke itney din intizar karey jitney ke her mahiney usey haiz aata tha jabke uska haiz sahih tha to is qadr dinon shumar karey aur un mein Namaz chhodey rahey, phir ghusl karey. kapdey se langot baandhey aur Namaz padhey ."
285,"Janab Urwa bin Zuber aur Umra , wo dono hi Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kartey hain ke Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko jo ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki saali aur Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki zojiyat mein thin , istihaza shuru ho gaya aur saat saal tak raha , unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye haiz nahin balke eik rag (ka khoon ( hai, to ghusl kar aur Namaz padh . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha Auzaai ne is hadees mein b-sanad zohri an (an) Urwa w umra an (an) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ye izafa kya ke Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko istihaza shuru ho gaya aur ye Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki zojiyat mein thi , usey saat saal tak ye aariza raha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hukm diya : ''jab haiz aa jaey to Namaz chhod do aur jab khatam ho jaey to ghusl karo aur Namaz padho . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke ye jumla ( إذا أقبلت الحيضة فدعي الصلاة وإذا أدبرت فاغتسلي وصلي ( Zohri ke shagirdon mein se Auzaai ke ilawa kisi ne zikr nahin kya hai. us riwayat ko Zohri se Amr bin Haris , Leis , Yunus , ibne-abi Zi'ib , Maamer , Ibrahim bin Saad , Suleman bin Kasir , ibn Is-haq aur Sufiyan bin Uena ne riwayat kya hai, magar ye hazraat ye jumla zikr nahin kartey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ye lafz sirf Hisham bin Urwa ne apney walid ke waastey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kiye hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke ibne-Uena ne ye izafa bhi kya hai ke aapney usey hukm diya : ''apney haiz ke dinon mein Namaz chhod dey.'' aur ye ibne-Uena ka weham hai. aur Muhammad bin Amr an (an) Zohri ki riwayat mein bhi kuch ( weham ( hai) jo uskey baad aa rahi hai) aur ye usi ke qarib qarib hai jo Auzaai ne apni hadees mein izafa kya hai."
286,"Janab Urwa bin Zuber , Fatima binte-abi Habish se raawi hain kaha ke unhen ( Fatima ko) istihaza aata tha, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''jab haiz ke khoon ka ho jo ke siyah rang ka hota hai aur pehchaana jata hai to jab ye aaye to Namaz se ruki raho aur jab doosra ho to wuzu karo aur Namaz padho . ye eik rag hoti hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Muhammad bin Musanna ne kaha ke ibne-abi Adi ne hamen apni kitab se aisey hi bayan kya (yani Urwa aur Fatima ke beech koi wastey nahin tha (aur baad mein jab apney hifz se riwayat kya to is sanad mein Aaysha ka zikr kya, kaha ke Fatima ko istihaza aata tha. phir ooper wali riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Anas bin Sirin ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se mustahaza ke baarey mein bayan kya ke jab wo khoob gehra surkh khoon dekhay to Namaz na padhey aur jab tuhur mehsoos karey agar-che eik ghadi hi ho to ghusl karey aur Namaz padhey . Mak-hool ne kaha hai ke aurton ke liye haiz ka maamla poshida nahin hota . ye khoon siyah aur gaadha hota hai. jab ye khatam ho jaey, gaadha na rahey aur zard rang ho jaey, to ye istihaza hota hai, to chahiye ke ghusl karey aur Namaz padhey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Hammad bin Zaid ne b-sanad Yahya bin Saeed, Saeed bin Musaiyab se mustahaza ke baarey mein riwayat kya hai : jab usey haiz aaye to Namaz chhod dey aur jab khatam ho jaey to ghusl karey aur Namaz padhey. Sumai aur kuch doosron ne Saeed bin Musaiyab se riwayat kya hai : ( mustahaza ( apney haiz ke dinon mein bethi rahey . aisey hi Hammad bin Salma ne Yahya bin Saeed ke wastey se Saeed bin Musaiyab se riwayat kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Yunus , Hasan Basri se bayan kartey hain : haiz wali ka khoon jab tool pakad jaey to haiz ke baad eik do din tak dekhay ( agar ruk jaey to behtar ( warna ye istihaza hai. Taimi ne Qatada se bayan kya ke jab uskey ayyame-haiz par paanch din ziyada ho jaeyn to Namaz padhna shuru kar dey. Taimi kehtey hain ke main dino ko kam kartey kartey do din tak pahuncha to kaha agar (maroof dinon sey) do din ziyada ho jaeyn to ye haiz hi ke hongey . ibn Sirin se uskey baarey mein puchha gaya to kaha ke aurton ko uska b-khoobi ilm hota hai."
287,"Imran bin Talha apni walida hamna binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain. hamna ne bataya ke mujhey bahut ziyada aur bada sakht istihaza hota tha. mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai ke aap se masla poochhun aur aap ko apni haalat bataun to maine aapko apni behan Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein paya . maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main aisi aurat hun jisey bahut sakht, shadeed istihaza hota hai, aapka uskey mutalliq kya irshad hai? usney mujhey Namaz aur rozey se bhi rok rakha hai. aapney farmaya : ''mera khayal hai ke tum rui rakh liya karo, us se khoon ruk jaeyga.'' us (Hamna) ne kaha : ye us se ziyada hota hai. aapney farmaya : ''to phir kapda baandh liya karo.'' maine kaha : ye us se bhi ziyada hota hai, meri to tilli ( dhaar ( behti hai. Rasulullah ne farmaya : ''main tumhen do baaten batata hun un mein se jo bhi ikhtiyar kar lo kafi hai. agar dono ki himmat ho to ye tumhen maloom hoga.'' aapney us se farmaya : ''ye darasal shetani kachokey hai. pas tum (her mahiney) Allah ke ilm ke mutabiq chhe ya saat din haiz ke shumar karo, phir ghusl kar lo, yahan tak ke jab tum apney aap ko paak saaf samjho to 23 ya 24 din raat Namaz padhti raho aur rozey rakho tumhen ye kafi hai aur her mahiney wesey hi kya karo jaisey ke aam aurten apney haiz aur tuhur ke dino mein karti hain. (doosri soorat (aur agar himmat ho to Zohar ko muakhkhar aur Asr ko jaldi karkey un dono ko jama kar lo aur unke liye eik ghusl karo. phir maghrib ko muakhkhar aur Isha ko jaldi kartey huey eik ghusl kar lo aur un namazon ko jama karkey padh lo. aur Fajr ki Namaz ke liye ( bhi) ghusl kar lo. agar tum ye kar sakti ho to kar liya karo aur rozey bhi rakhti jao.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur ye (doosri) soorat un dono mein se merey nazdik ziyada pasandida hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha us riwayat ko Amr bin Sabit ne ibne-Aqeel se naqal kya aur kaha : hamna ne kaha : ''ye soorat merey nazdik ziyada pasandida hai.'' us qol ko usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farman nahin bataya, balke hamna ka qol kaha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Amr bin Sabit raafzi tha aur ye qol Yahya bin Mueen se zikr kya. (lekin wo hadees mein sacha tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maine Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) se suna kehtey they ke ibne-Aqeel ki hadees ke baarey mein merey dil mein kuch (tardeed) hai."
288,"Janab Urwa bin Zuber aur Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) zauja Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se raawi hain, Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) jo ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki saali aur Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya thin, unko saat saal tak istihaza raha. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us baarey mein masla puchha to aapney farmaya : ''ye haiz nahin balke eik rag (ka khoon) hai, lihaza ghusl karo aur Namaz padho.'' Hazrat Aaysha bayan karti hain ke wo apni behan Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey main eik lagan mein ghusl kartin, to khoon ki surkhi pani par chha jati thi."
289,"Umra bint Abdur-Rehman, Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) se yehi hadees riwayat karti hain. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : chunanche wo her Namaz ke liye ghusl kya karti thin."
290,"Urwa, Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se yehi hadees riwayat kartey hain. us mein kaha : chunanche wo her Namaz ke liye ghusl kya karti thin. (ikhtilaf sanadon ka bayan) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye hadees Qasim bin Mabrur ne Yunus sey, wo ibn shahab sey, wo Umra sey, wo Aaysha se unhoney Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki hai. aur aisey hi Maamer ne Zohri se usney Umra se usney Aaisha se riwayat ki hai lekin Maamer ne kabhi ( an (an) umra an (an) أم حبيبة ( kaha hai aur aisey hi Ibrahim bin Saad aur ibne-Uena ( dono ( ne Zohri se wo Umra se usney Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki hai. ibne-Uena ne apni riwayat mein kaha ke) Zohri ne ( ye nahin kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey ghusl kerney ka hukm diya tha."
291,"Janab Urwa aur Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman ( dono ( Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain ke Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ko saat saal tak istihaza raha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen hukm diya ke ghusl karen, chunanche wo her Namaz ke liye ghusl kya karti thin. Auzaai ne bhi aisey hi riwayat kya hai ke Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : wo her Namaz ke liye ghusl kya karti thin ."
292,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein istihaza aata raha , to aapney unhen her Namaz ke liye ghusl kerney ka hukm diya aur hadees bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : usey abul-Waleed Tiyalisi ne riwayat kya hai, magar maine un se suna nahin hai) balke bilwaasta suna hai. ( ) Tiyalisi ne ( Suleman bin Kasir se wo Zohri se wo Urwa se wo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain, kaha : Zenab binte-Jahash ko istihaza ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : '' her Namaz ke liye ghusl kya karo.'' aur hadees bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : usey abdus-Samad ne Suleman bin Kasir se riwayat kya to kaha : '' her Namaz ke liye wuzu kya karo.'' magar ye abdus-Samad ka weham hai. us baarey mein abul-Waleed ka qol sahih hai."
293,Janab abu-Salma kehtey hain ke mujh se Zenab binte-abi Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan kya ke eik aurat ko bahut ziyada khoon aata tha aur wo Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anha) ki zojiyat mein thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hukm diya ke '' her Namaz ke waqt ghusl karey aur Namaz padha karey.'' ( Yahya bin abi kaseer ne kaha ke mujhey abu-Salma ne bataya ke) umme-Bakr ne mujhey khabar di ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us aurat ke baarey mein farmaya jisey ke tuhur shuru honey ke baad koi shak wali keyfiyat darpesh ho.'' beshak ye rag (ka khoon) hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ibne-Aqeel ki riwayat mein dono baaten jama hain : aapney farmaya : ''agar taqat rakhti ho to her Namaz ke liye ghusl kar liya karo warna jama kar lo.'' jaisey ke Qasim ne apni riwayat mein bayan kya. aur yehi qol Saeed bin Jubair ne Hazrat Ali aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) se naqal kya hai.
294,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main eik aurat ko istihaza aaney laga to usey hukm diya gaya ke namaze-Asr ko jaldi aur Zohar ko muakhkhar karey. aur un dono ( namazon (ke liye eik ghusl karey. aur maghrib ko muakhkhar aur Isha ko jaldi karey aur un dono ke liye eik ghusl karey aur Fajr ki Namaz ke liye eik ghusl karey. maine (yani Shoba ne ( Abdur-Rehman se kaha : kya ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marwi (bayan) hai? unhoney kaha : main tujhey jo bhi bayan karta hun wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi ki hadees hoti hai.
295,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Sehla bint Suhel (Raziallahu anha) ko istihazey ka aariza ho gaya to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ayen . aapney unhen hukm diya ke her Namaz ke liye ghusl kya karen, magar jab wo us se mashaqqat mein pad gaeen to unhen hukm diya ke Zohar w Asr ki Namaz eik ghusl ke sath jama keren aur maghrib w Isha ko eik ghusl ke sath aur subh ke liye eik ghusl kya karen. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha us riwayat ko ibne-Uena ne Abdur-Rehman bin Qasim , sey, unhoney apney walid se riwayat kya hai. kaha : eik aurat ko istihaza ho gaya , usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aapney usko hukm diya. aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya."
296,"Sayeda Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anha) , kehti hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Fatima binte-abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) ko itni muddat se istihaza ho raha hai aur wo Namaz nahin padh saki . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Subhanallah ! ye shetani asar hai. usey chahiye ke tab mein bethey , agar pani par zardi ghalib ho to chahiye ke Zohar aur Asr ke liye eik ghusl karey aur maghrib aur Isha ke liye eik ghusl karey aur Fajr ke liye eik ghusl karey aur unke beech wuzu karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha is hadees ko Mujahid ne ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kya ke jab us par) her Namaz ke liye ( ghusl mushkil ho gaya to usey hukm diya ke do namazon ko jama kar liya karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : aur usey Ibrahim Nakhai ne ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se naqal kya hai aur Ibrahim Nakhai aur aisey hi Abdullah bin Shaddad ka bhi yehi qol hai."
297,Janab Adi bin Sabit apney walid se wo us ( Adi (ke naana se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se raawi hain ke aapney mustahaza ke baarey mein farmaya : '' apney haiz ke dinon ki namazein chhod dey phir ghusl karey aur Namaz padhna shuru kar dey aur her Namaz ke liye wuzu kya karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Usman ne ziyada kya : '' rozey rakhey aur Namaz padhey .''
298,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo kehti hain ke Fatima binte-abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ayen aur (raawi ne) unka waqia zikr kya. aapney farmaya : '' phir ghusl karo aur phir her Namaz ke liye wuzu karo aur Namaz padhti raho.''"
299,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) mustahaza ke baarey mein marwi (bayan) hai ke wo ghusl karey yani eik hi baar. phir ayyame-haiz aaney tak wuzu hi karti rahey.
300,"Janab Masruq ki ehliya Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat karti hain, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke manind bayan kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke mazkura sadar riwayaat Adi bin Sabit , Aamash Habib aur Ayub abul-Ala sab zaeef hain, sahih nahin hain. Aamash b-waasta Habib ki hadees (mazkura 298 ( zaeef honey ki daleel ye hai ke Hafs bin Ghiyas , Aamash se moquf bayan kartey hain aur Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Habib ki hadees ke marfoo honey ka inkar kya hai, neez asbaat ne Aamash se Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) par moquf zikr kya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke ibn Dawud ne Aamash se sirf pehla hissey marfoo riwayat kya hai aur is baat ka inkar kya hai ke us mein her Namaz ke liye wuzu ka bayan ho. Habib ki is hadees ke zaeef honey ki) doosri) daleel ye bhi hai ke «زهری an عروة an عائشة» ki mustahaza wali riwayat mein hai unhoney kaha ke wo her Namaz ke liye ghusl kya karti thin . jabke abu-Yaqzan ne b-sanad «عدي بن ثابت an Abeeh an علي» aur Ammar maula bani Hashim ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se aur Abdul-Malik bin Maisra, Bayan bin Bishr , Mughira , Faraas aur Majaalid ne Shobi se hadees Qumair mein Hazrat Aaysha se bayan kya hai ke wo her Namaz ke liye wuzu karey. Dawud aur Aasim ki riwayat mein jo شعبي an قمير an عائشة se marwi (bayan) hai ke her roz eik ghusl karey. jabke Hisham bin Urwa عن أبيه ki riwayat hai ke mustahaza her Namaz ke liye ghusl karey. aur ye sab ahadis zaeef hain, siwaye ( un teen ahadis ke . yani ( hadees Qumair (zauja Masruq), hadees Ammar maula bani Hashim aur hadees Hisham bin Urwa an Abeeh . aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka maroof qol ghusl ka hai."
301,"Sumae maula abi Bakr se marwi (bayan) hai ke Qaaqaa aur Zaid bin Aslam ne mujhey Saeed bin Musaiyab ke paas bheja ke un se mustahaza ke ghusl ke baarey mein sawal karun. to unhoney kaha ke Zohar se Zohar tak ke liye ghusl karey aur) uskey beech ( baqi her Namaz ke liye wuzu karey aur agar us par khoon ghalib ho to kapdey ka langot baandh liya karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke ibne-Umar aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu Anhuma) se ( bhi yehi ( marwi (bayan) hai ke Zohar se Zohar tak ke liye wuzu karey aur aisey hi Dawud aur Aasim ne Shobi se wo apni zauja se wo Qumair ( zauja Masruq ( se usney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kya hai, magar Dawud ne kaha ke '' her roz ghusl karey '' aur Aasim ki riwayat mein hai ke '' Zohar ke waqt ghusl karey '' aur yehi qol hai Salim bin Abdullah , Hasan aur Ata ka . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Malik kehtey hain ke ibn Musaiyab ki hadees '' Zohar se Zohar tak '' ke baarey mein mera guman hai ke ye darasal '' tuhur se tuhur tak '' hai lekin kisi ko weham hua to usney usey '' Zohar se Zohar tak '' bana diya. jabkey Miswar bin Abdul-Malik ne us riwayat ko '' tuhur se tuhur tak '' hi bayan kya hai, magar logon ne usey '' Zohar se Zohar tak '' bana diya hai."
302,Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mustahaza ka haiz jab khatam ho jaey to wo her roz ghusl kya karey aur thodi si oon ghi ya zaitun ke tel mein tar karkey hamool kar liya karey. (yani sharmgaah mein rakh liya karey.)
303,"Muhammad bin Usman ne Qasim bin Muhammad se mustahaza ke baarey mein sawal kya to unhoney kaha ke apney haiz ke dino mein Namaz chhodey rahey, phir (unke khatam honey par) ghusl karey aur Namaz padhna shuru kar dey aur phir un dino ke darmiyan (moqa b-mauqa) ghusl karti rahey ."
304,"Sayeda Fatima binte-abi Habish (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhen istihaza hota tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : ''jab haiz ka khoon aaye aur ye siyah rang ka hota hai aur pehchaana jata hai, to jab ye shuru ho to Namaz se ruk jao aur jab doosra ho to wuzu karo aur Namaz padho . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke ibn Musanna ne kaha ke hamen ye hadees ibne-abi Adi ne apney hifz se bayan ki to iski sanad mein Aaisha ka izafa kya (yani Urwa an (an) Aaisha an (an) Fatima ( . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Ala bin Musaiyab aur Shoba se marwi (bayan) hai) dono ( hukm se wo abu-Jafar se riwayat kartey hain. Ala ne marfooan Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aur Shoba ne abu-Jafar se mauqoofan bayan kya : ''wo her Namaz ke liye wuzu karey.''"
305,Janab Ikrima bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Umme-Habiba bint Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko istihaza shuru ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hukm diya : '' apney ayyame-haiz (ke khatam honey (ka intizar karey. phir ghusl karey aur Namaz padhna shuru kar dey . agar ( khoon ke ilawa ( koi napaki mehsoos karey to wuzu karey aur Namaz padhey.''
306,"Rabeea (bin Abdur-Rehman , al-Maaruf Rabeea raai, Taabai ( se manqul hai ke wo mustahaza par her Namaz ke liye tajdeed wuzu ke qaail na they, siwaey iske ke usey khoon ke ilawa koi aur hadas laahiq ho to wuzu karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Janab Malik bin Anas (Rahimahullah) ka bhi yehi qol hai."
307,"umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baiat ki thi , bayan karti hain ke ham tuhur shuru ho janey ke baad mailey ya peeley se pani aaney ko kuch na samajhti thin ."
308,Janab Muhammad bin Sirin ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) se usi ke misl riwayat kya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : umme-Huzail se murad Hafsa bint Sirin hain. unke bete ka naam Huzail aur shohar ka naam Abdur-Rehman tha.
309,Janab Ikrima ne bayan kya ke Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ko istihaza hota tha aur unka shohar un se mujaamiat kya karta tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Yahya bin Mueen ne Muallaa ko suqa (qabile-bharosa) kaha hai. jabke Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal us se kuch riwayat na kartey they kyonkey wo raey aur qiyas (guman) ki taraf maael they.
310,"Janab Ikrima, Hamna binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhen istihaza aata tha aur unka shohar un se mubashrat karta tha."
311,ummul-momenin Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke nifaas wali aurten Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein zachgi ke baad chaalis din ya chaalis raaten bethi rehti thin aur chehrey ki rangat badal janey (ya jhaaiyaan padney ( ki wajeh se ham apney chehron par waras malti thin .) ye zard rang ki eik booti hoti hai jo bator ubtan istimal ki jati hai. (
312,"Kasir bin Ziyad kehtey hain ke mujh se Azdiya yani Mussa ne bayan kya, wo kehti hain ke main hajj ko gaee to Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaee . maine kaha : aey ummul-momenin ! Samra bin Jundub ( sahabi Rasool ( aurton ko hukm detey hain ke ayyame-haiz ki namazon ki qaza kya karen. unhoney kaha : koi qaza na karen. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aurton mein se koi nifaas se hoti to chaalis raat bethi rehti . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey un dino ki namazon ki qaza kerney ka hukm na detey they. Muhammad bin Hatim ne kaha ke us khatoon rawiya ka naam Mussa hai. aur uski kunniyat umma-Bussa hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Kasir bin Ziyad ki kunniyat abu-Sehal hai."
313,"Umayya binte-abi Salat qabeela bani ghifaar ki eik khatoon se riwayat karti hain ( Salma ne kaha ( merey Shekh ne mujh se unka naam zikr kya tha ( magar main bhool gaya ( wo bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey apni sawari par paalaan ke pichley hissey par bitha liya aur qasam Allah ki ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subh ke waqt hi oontni se utrey . aapney sawari ko bithaya aur main bhi paalaan ke peechey se utri to us par merey khoon ka nishan tha aur ye mera pehla haiz tha. kehti hain ke mujhey haya aai aur main oontni se lag gaee . chunanche jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne meri keyfiyat dekhi aur khoon bhi) to bhaanp gaey (aur farmaya : ''kya hua ? shayad ke tujhey haiz aa gaya hai? ''maine kaha : haan ! aapney farmaya : '' apney aap ko durust kar lo aur pani ka eik bartan lekar us mein kuch namak mila lo aur paalaan ko jo khoon laga hai usey dho dalo aur phir apni jagah Sawar ho jao .'' wo bayan karti hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar Fateh kar liya to hamen maale-fai mein se kuch inayat farmaya. wo kehti hain ke wo jab bhi haiz se paak hotin to pani mein namak mila liya karti thin , yahan tak ke unhoney maut ke waqt wasiyat ki ke unke ghusl ke pani mein namak milaaya jaey."
314,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan aain aur kehney lagin : aey Allah ke Rasool ! jab ham mein se koi haiz se paak ho, to kaisey ghusl karey ? aapney farmaya : '' beri ke pattey mila pani ley aur wuzu karey, phir apna sar dhoey aur khoob maley yahan tak ke pani baalon ki jadon tak pahunch jaey, phir baqi jism par pani bahaaey, phir rui ki potli ley aur us se tahaarat hasil karey.'' kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Rasool ! us se kaisey tahaarat hasil karun ? Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main samajh gaee ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kya kehna chahtey hain, to maine usey bataya ke usey khoon ke maqam par rakho ."
315,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai unhoney ( Hazrat Aaisha ne ( khawatin ansaar ka zikr kya aur unki madah ki aur zikre-khair kya, kaha ke un mein se eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai... aur ooper wali hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya, magar us riwayat mein hai : '' kastoori ka phaha ley.'' Musaddad ne kaha ke abu-Awaana ( فرصة (ka lafz bayan kartey they aur abul-ahwas ( قرصة ( ."
316,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Asma ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat kya. us mein hai ke kastoori ka phaha ley. wo kehney lagi ke us se kis tarah tahaarat hasil karun ? aapney farmaya : '' Subhanallah ! us se pakizgi hasil kar .'' aur aap alehissalam ne kapdey se apna munh chupa liya . aur us mein izafa hai ke usney ghusle-janabat ke mutalliq puchha : aapney farmaya : '' apna pani lo aur us se khoob achi tarah mukammal wuzu karo, phir apney sar par pani dalo , phir usey malo, yahan tak ke baalon ki jadon tak pahunch jaey. phir baqi jism par pani bahao .'' Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ansaar ki aurten bahut khoob hain, unhen deen ke masayel daryaft kerney aur samajhney mein haya maane (rukawat) nahin hoti."
317,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Usaid bin Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) aur kuch logon ko wo haar dhoondney bheja jo mujh se gum ho gaya tha, (us beech mein) Namaz ka waqt ho gaya to unhoney baghair wuzu ke Namaz padh li . phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan aaye aur apni baat batai , to tayammum ki aayat nazil hui . ibne-Nufail ne is qadr mazeed bayan kya ke Usaid ne un (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( se kaha : Allah aap par rehem farmaey. aap ko jab bhi koi pareshani laahiq hui jo aapko naagawar hui magar Allah ne usey musalmanon ke liye mufeed bana diya aur aap ke liye bhi us mein se koi raah nikal di."
318,"Saiyedna Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai wo bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein namaze-Fajr ke liye tayammum kya to (us ki soorat ye rahi ke) unhoney apney haath mitti par maarey aur apney chehron par pherey , phir dusri baar maarey aur apney purey baazuon par pherey kandhon tak aur andar ki taraf se baghlon tak ."
319,"Suleman bin Dawud Mehri aur Abdul-Malik bin Shuaib ne ibne-Wahab ke wastey se mazkura hadees ke misl bayan kya, kaha ke musalman uthey aur apney haath mitti par maarey lekin mitti se kuch na pakda . mazkura hadees ke qarib qarib zikr kya aur us mein kandhon aur baghlon ka zikr nahin kya. ibn Leis ne kaha : kohniyon se ooper tak ( masah kya. ("
320,"Janab Ubaidullah bin Abdullah Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se wo Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu Anhuma) se raawi hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maqam '' aulatul Jaish'' main aakhir raat mein padaaw dala . Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aap ke sath thin . to unka haar jo ke zifaar ke ghongon ka tha, toot kar gir gaya. us haar ki talash ne logon ko) aagey chalney sey) rok liya , yahan tak ke subh roshan ho gaee aur unke paas pani bhi na tha, is par abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko (Hazrat Aaisha par) ghussa aa gaya aur kaha : tune logon ko rok rakha hai aur unke paas pani bhi nahin hai. to us moqe par Allah taala ne apney Rasool par paak mitti se tahaarat kerney ki rukhsat nazil farmaai. chunanche musalman Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath uthey aur apney haath zameen par maarey aur utha liye , haathon mein koi mitti na uthai aur phir unhen apney chehron aur baazuon par kandhon tak aur andar ki taraf se baghlon tak pher liya . ibn Yahya ne apni riwayat mein mazeed kaha ke ibne-shahab ne apni hadees mein kaha ke magar log is hadees ka aetbar nahin kartey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ibne-Is-haq ne aisey hi riwayat kya hai, us mein Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai aur do dafa haath maarna bayan kya, jaisey ke Yunus ne zikr kya hai. aur is riwayat ko Maamer ne Zohri se riwayat kya to us mein bhi ''do dafa maarna'' hai. Imam Malik ki sanad yun hai an (an) zohri an (an) Ubaidullah bin Abdullah an (an) Abeeh an (an) Ammar aur aisey hi Abu-Uwais ne Zohri se riwayat kya. aur ibne-Uena ko is sanad mein shak hua to eik baar yun bayan ki : an (an) Ubaidullah an (an) Abeeh ya an (an) Ubaidullah an (an) ibne-Abbas aur eik baar , an (an) Abeeh kaha aur eik baar an (an) ibne-Abbas kaha . ibne-Uena ko us mein Zohri se samaa, mein iztirab hua hai magar un mein se kisi eik ne bhi is hadees mein '' do dafa haath maarney '' ka zikr nahin kya, siwaye unke jinka maine naam liya ."
321,"Shaqiq kehtey hain ke main Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood aur Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke darmiyan betha hua tha ke Abu-Musa ne kaha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! farmaiye , agar koi aadmi junbi ho jaey aur eik mahiney tak pani na miley to kya wo tayammum nahin kerega ? ( Abdullah ne kaha ( : nahin, agar-che wo eik mahiney tak pani na paey . Abu-Musa ne kaha : to aap sura maayda ki us aayat ke baarey mein kya kahengey : ( فَلَمْ تَجِدُوا مَاءً فَتَيَمَّمُوا صَعِيدًا طَيِّبًا ( ''agar pani na pao to paak mitti se tayammum kar lo .'' Hazrat Abdullah ne kaha : agar unhen uski rukhsat de-di jaey to aen mumkin hai ke jab bhi pani thanda hua to ye mitti se tayammum kerney lagengey. Abu-Musa ne un se kaha : achcha to aap isi wajeh se usey makruh jantey hain? kaha ke haan! Abu-Musa ne kaha : kya aapney Ammar ki wo baat nahin suni jo unhoney umr se kahi thi? ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey kisi kaam se bheja aur main junbi ho gaya aur pani na mila to main mitti mein lot-pot ho gaya jaisey ke janwer lot-pot hota hai, phir main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur apni baat batai to aapney farmaya : '' tumhen to bas yehi kafi tha ke is tarah kar letey.'' phir aapney apna haath zameen par maara , phir usey jhaada, phir apney baaeyn ko daain par aur daain ko baaeyn par hatheliyon par phera, phir apney chehrey ka masah kya. to Abdullah (bin Masood) ne un se kaha : to kya aapney nahin dekha ke umr ne Ammar ki baat par qana-at nahin ki ."
322,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Abza kehtey hain ke main Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha ke eik aadmi unke paas aaya aur kaha : ham kabhi-kabhi mahina do mahina aisey maqamat par hotey hain ( jahan wafir pani nahin hota ( to umr ne kaha : main to aisi soorat mein Namaz nahin padhunga , yahan tak ke pani pa lun . Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey ameerul-momeneen ! kya aap ko yaad nahin ke jab main aur aap oont charaney gaey they aur ham junbi ho gaey they to main ( mitti mein) lot pot ho gaya tha, phir ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur ye qissa zikr kya to aapney farmaya tha : '' tumhen yehi kafi tha ke aisey kar letey aur aapney apney dono haath zameen par maarey , phir un dono mein phunk maari aur unhen apney chehrey par phera aur haathon par bhi aadhi kalaaii tak .'' to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Ammar ! Allah se daro ( aisi baat kyon kehtey ho ( to Ammar ne kaha : aey ameerul-momeneen ! agar aap kahen to qasam Allah ki us waqie ka kabhi zikr nahin karunga. to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hergiz nahin, qasam Allah ki ! us mein ham tumhen hi tumhari baat ka zimmedar banatey hain."
323,"Janab Salma bin Kuheil , ibn Abza se wo Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir sey, is hadees mein hai, kaha ke aey Ammar ! tumhen to bas is tarah kafi tha. phir apney dono haath zameen par maarey . phir eik ko doosrey par maara aur phir apney chehrey aur aadhi kalaaiyon tak pher liye , kohniyon tak nahin ley gaey aur haath zameen par eik hi baar maarey . Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : is hadees ko Wakee ne Aamash se unhoney Salma bin Kuheil se unhoney Abdur-Rehman bin Abza se riwayat kya. aur Jarir ne Aamash se unhoney Salma se unhoney Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abza yani unhoney apney walid se."
324,"Janab ibne-Abdur-Rehman bin Abza apney walid se wo Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se yehi qissa bayan kartey hain. us mein kaha : '' tumhen yehi kafi tha.'' aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna haath zameen par maara , phir us mein phunk maari aur us se apney chehrey aur dono haathon ka masah kya. Salma ko shak hua hai, kaha : mujhey maloom nahin ke us riwayat mein '' kohniyon tak hai, ya '' hatheliyon tak .''"
325,"Janab Shoba ne apni sanad se ye hadees bayan ki aur kaha : phir us mein phunk maari aur us se apney chehrey aur haathon ka kohniyon tak ya kalaaiyon tak masah kya. Shoba ne kaha : Salma dono haath, chehre aur dono kalaaiyaan bayan kya kartey they. to eik din Mansoor ne un se kaha ke jo aap kehtey hain us mein ghor kar lijiye.'' kalaaiyon'' ka zikr aap ke ilawa aur koi nahin karta."
326,"Janab ibne-Abdur-Rehman bin Abza apney walid se wo Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, is hadees mein kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhen yehi kafi tha ke apney dono haath zameen par maartay aur apney chehrey aur haathon ka masah kar letey .'' aur hadees bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : usko Shoba ne Husain se unhoney abu-Malik se riwayat kya, kaha ke maine Ammar ko khutbey mein aisey hi bayan kartey suna, magar unhoney kaha '' phunk nahin maari .'' aur Husain bin Muhammad ne Shoba se unhoney Hakam se riwayat kya to kaha : '' apney dono haath zameen par maarey aur phunk maari .''"
327,"Janab Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abza apney walid se bayan kartey hain wo Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) sey, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se tayammum ke baarey mein puchha to aapney mujhey hukm diya ke chehrey aur haathon ke liye eik hi dafa haath maarun ."
328,"Janab Aban kehtey hain ke Qatada se safar mein tayammum ke baarey mein puchha gaya to unhoney kaha ke mujh se eik bayan kerney waley ne Shobi sey, unhoney Abdur-Rehman bin Abza sey, unhoney Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu Anhuma) se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kohniyon tak.''"
329,"Umair maula ibne-Abbas ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se suna, wo kehtey they ke main aur ummul-momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghulam Abdullah bin Yasar aaye aur Abul-Jaheem bin Haris bin Simma Ansari ke yahan gaey to Abul-Jaheem ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) biare-jamal ( maqam ( ki janib se tashrif la rahey they. aap ko eik aadmi mila aur usney aap ko salam kya, magar aapney uskey salam ka jawab na diya, yahan tak ke aap deewar ke paas aaye aur apney chehrey aur haathon ka masah kya aur phir uskey salam ka jawab diya."
330,"Janab Naafe bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath eik kaam ke liye Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke yahan gaya , to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne apna kaam pura kar liya . us din unki baaton mein se eik ye thi ke eik gali main eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzra jabkey aap peshab ya pakhaney se farigh ho kar aaye they, to usney aap ko salam kaha, magar aapney jawab na diya, yahan tak ke jab wo gali mein aakhon se ojhal honey ke qarib hua , to aapney apney dono haath deewar par maarey aur apney chehrey par pherey, phir dusri baar maarey aur apni kalaaiyon par pherey tab uskey salam ka jawab diya, aur farmaya : ''terey salam ka jawab na deney ki wajeh sirf ye thi ke main taahir na tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Ahmed bin Hanbal ko suna, wo kehtey they ke Muhammad bin Sabit ne tayammum ke baarey main eik ''munkar'' hadees riwayat ki hai. ibne-Daasa kehtey hain ke Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Muhammad bin Sabit ki us qissey mein kisi ne mutaabiat ( taeed ( nahin ki ke '' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do dafa haath maarey .'' balke usey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka amal bayan kya gaya hai."
331,"Janab Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se ye hadees bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pakhaney se farigh ho kar aaye to aap ko eik aadmi mila . us waqt aap jamal kunwe ke paas they. usney aap ko salam kaha magar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko jawab na diya, yahan tak ke deewar ke paas aaye aur deewar par apna haath rakha , phir apney chehrey aur haathon ka masah kya, phir aapney uskey salam ka jawab diya."
332,"Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan kuch bakriyan jama ho gaeen to aapney farmaya : ''aey abu-Zar ! unhen lekar bahir jangal mein chaley jaao .'' chunanche main rabza ke baadiye mein chala gaya. pas main junbi ho gaya to 5-6 din wahan raha phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aa gaya. aapney kaha : '' abu-Zar ! '' to main khamosh raha . aapney farmaya : '' tujhey teri maa gum karey, abu-Zar ! teri maa ke liye afsos .'' aapney meri khatir eik kaali si londi ko bulwaaya to wo eik bada piyala ley aai , us mein pani tha. usney mujhey kapdey se parda kar diya aur) dusri taraf sey) main apni sawari ki ot mein ho gaya aur ghusl kya to (us tarah ( merey sar se goya eik pahad utar gaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' paak mitti musalman ke liye tahaarat ka zaria hai bhale hi das saal tak (pani na paey ( phir jab tumhen pani miley to usey apney jism par dalo . yaqinan ye behtar hai.'' Musaddad ne bayan kya ke ye bakriyan sadqey ki thin . aur Amr ki hadees ziyada kamil hai."
333,"Janab abu-Qulaba bani Aamir ke eik shakhs se riwayat kartey hain, us shakhs ka bayan hai ke maine Islam qubul kar liya magar merey deen ne mujhey fikr mein dal diya. chunanche main Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya, to abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke maine Madina ki aab w hawa ko apney liye na-muwaafiq paya . pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey liye chand oonton aur bakriyon ka hukm diya (ke usey de-di jaeyn (aur mujhey farmaya : '' unka doodh piyo .'' Hammad ki riwayat mein hai : ''mujhey shak hai ke us mein peshab ka bayan hai ya nahin .'' Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke main pani se door hota tha aur merey sath meri ehliya bhi thi aur mujhey janabat pahunchti thi to main pani ke baghair hi Namaz padh leta tha. phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya, do-pehar ka waqt tha aur aap Sahaba kiram ke sath mein masjid ke saye mein tashrif farma they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( mujhey dekh kar) farmaya : '' abu-Zar ?'' maine kaha : ji , main to halak ho gaya , aey Allah ke Rasool ! farmaya : '' kis chiz ne halak kar diya tujhey ?'' maine kaha : main pani se door hota tha, biwi merey sath thi aur mujhey janabat pahunchti thi to main baghair ghusl kiye Namaz padhta raha . chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey liye pani laney ka hukm farmaya. eik siyah rang ki londi eik bada piyala ley aai , pani us mein chhalak raha tha aur wo puri tarah bhara hua bhi na tha, to maine apney oont ki ot mein ho kar ghusl kya aur khidmat mein hazir ho gaya. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey abu-Zar ! paak mitti paak kerney wali hai agar-che tujhey das saal tak pani na miley aur jab pani mil jaey to usey apni jild par dalo . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is hadees ko Hammad bin Zaid ne Ayub se riwayat kya to us mein '' oonton ke peshab '' ka zikr nahin kya aur ye sahih ( bhi) nahin hai. haan unke peshab ke baarey mein sirf Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat hai (yani hadees عرنين ( jiski riwayat mein ehle-Basra munfarid (bilkul alag) hain."
334,"Abdur-Rehman bin Jubair Hazrat Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke ghazwa zaat salaasil mein mujhey eik thandi raat ehtilaam ho gaya , mujhey andesha hua ke agar maine ghusl kya to halak ho jaunga , chunanche maine tayammum kar liya aur apney sathiyon ko subh ki Namaz padhaai . unhoney ye waqia Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein zikr kya to aapney puchha : ''aey Amr ! kya to ney junbi hotey huey apney sathiyon ki jamaat karaai thi ?'' maine bataya ke kis wajeh se maine ghusl nahin kya tha aur maine ye bhi kaha ke maine Allah ka farman suna hai : ( { وَلَا تَقْتُلُوا . . . . . } ( '' apney aap ko qatl na karo, Allah tum par bahut hi meharban hai.'' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hans padey aur kuch na kaha . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Abdur-Rehman bin Jubair Misri hai, khaarija bin Huzafa ka ghulam hai. aur ye ibne-Jubair bin Nafair nahin hai."
335,"Janab abu-Qais maula Amr bin al-Aas se manqul hai ke Hazrat Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) eik fauji muhim par they. aur misl saabiq hadees bayan ki . kaha ke unhoney apni sharmgaah aur uske aas-paas ke hissey ko dhoya aur Namaz wala wuzu kya aur unhen Namaz padhaai . aur mazkura baala ki manind bayan kya aur tayammum ka zikr nahin kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye qissa Auzaai sey, unhoney Hassaan bin Atiya se riwayat kya hai to us mein hai ke '' unhoney tayammum kya. ''"
336,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke ham eik safar mein nikley to ham mein se eik shakhs ko pathar lag gaya aur uskey sar mein zakhm ho gaya , phir usey ehtilaam ( bhi) ho gaya. usney apney sathiyon se puchha : kya merey liye koi ijazat hai ke main tayammum kar lun ? unhoney kaha ke ham tumharey liye koi rukhsat nahin paatey jabkey tum ko pani par qudrat hasil hai. chunanche usney ghusl kar liya aur mar gaya. jab ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey , aap ko uski khabar di gaee , to aapney farmaya : '' unhoney usko qatl kar dala . Allah unhen halak karey, unhoney poochh kyon na liya, jabke unhen ilm na tha, beshak aajiz ( jahil ( ki shifa sawal kar leney mein hai. us shakhs ke liye yehi kafi tha ke tayammum kar leta aur apney zakhm par patti baandhey rehta. Musa ko shak hua ke يعصر ka lafz bola ya يعصب ka , ( maani , dono ka patti baandhna hai) phir us par masah karta aur baqi sara jism dho leta.''"
337,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik shakhs ko zakhm lag gaya , phir usey ehtilaam ho gaya , to usey ghusl kerney ka hukm diya gaya. chunanche usney ghusl kya aur mar gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko uski khabar pahunchi to aapney farmaya : '' unhoney usko maar dala , Allah unhen halak karey. kya jahil ki shifa sawal kar lena nahin hai? ''"
338,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehtey hain ke do aadmi safar par nikley aur Namaz ka waqt ho gaya. unke paas pani nahin tha. unhoney paak mitti se tayammum karkey Namaz padh li, magar abhi Namaz ka waqt baqi tha ke pani mil gaya to un mein se eik ne wuzu karkey Namaz dohra li aur doosrey ne na dohrai. phir wo dono Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur aapko apna waqia bataya, to aapney us sey, jisney Namaz nahin dohrai thi, farmaya : ''tum ne sunnat par amal kya aur tumharey liye tumhari Namaz kafi ho gaee.'' aur jisney wuzu karkey Namaz dohrai thi , usey farmaya : '' tumharey liye dohra ajr hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : ibn Naafe ke ilawa eik doosrey sahab ne usey Leis se unhoney umaira bin abi naajiya se unhoney Bakr bin suwaada se unhoney Ata bin Yasar se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees mein abu-Saeed ka zikr mehfooz nahin hai aur ye hadees mursal hai."
339,Janab Ata bin Yasar se riwayat hai ke be-shak Rasulullah ke Sahaba mein se do aadmi ( safar par nikley (aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya.
340,"Janab abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ka bayan hai ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko khabar di ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) eik moqe par khutba juma irshad farma rahey they ke eik aadmi aaya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya tum log Namaz se rukey rehtey ho? (aur takheer se aatey ho?) us aadmi ne jawab diya : iskey siwa kuch nahin hua ke maine Azan suni, fauran wuzu kya (aur hazir ho gaya) to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aur sirf wuzu? kya tum logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye irshad nahin suna : ''jab tum mein se koi juma ke liye aaye to ghusl karey.''"
341,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Juma ke roz ghusl karna her baligh par wajib hai.''
342,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain ke aapney farmaya : '' her baligh par Juma ke liye jana ( lazim ( hai. aur her wo shakhs jis par Juma ke liye jana (lazim) hai, us par ghusl hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : agar kisi ne tulu Fajr ke baad ghusl kar liya , chahey janabat hi se ho to ye uskey liye ghusl Juma se kafi hai."
343,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney Juma ke roz ghusl kya aur behtareen kapdey zeb tan kiye aur khushbu bhi lagai agar muyassar ho to , phir Juma ke liye aaya aur logon ki gardanen na phalaangein , phir ( nafli ( Namaz padhi jo uskey liye muqaddar ki gaee , phir khamosh raha jab Imam ( khutbey ke liye ( nikla , yahan tak ke apni Namaz se farigh hua to ye uskey liye us Jumey aur sabiqa Jumey ke beech ( sadir honey waley gunahon (ka kaffara hai. ( abu-Salma ne ( kaha : Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they ke balke mazeed teen din aur bhi . (yani sirf Juma se Juma tak , aath dino ka kaffara hi nahin, balke teen din mazeed bhi , yun giyara din huey aur kasar chhod den to 10 din , kyonkey ( wo kaha kartey they ke her neki das guna ajr ki hamil hoti hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : abu-Salma ki riwayat ziyada kamil hai aur Hammad ne apni riwayat mein Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka kalam naqal nahin kya."
344,Janab Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Saeed Khudri apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Juma ke roz ghusl her baligh par) lazim ( hai aur miswak aur khushbu ( bhi) jo usey muyassar ho.'' Buker ne Abdur-Rehman ka zikr nahin kya aur khushbu ke baarey mein kaha : ''khuwah biwi hi ki ho.'' (yani zarur istimal karey.)
345,"Hazrat Aus bin Aus Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna farmatey they : '' jisney Juma ke roz ghusl kya aur khoob achi tarah kya aur jaldi aaya aur) khutbe mein) awwal waqt pahuncha , pedal chal ke aaya aur sawar na hua , Imam se qarib ho kar betha aur ghor se suna aur laghw se bacha , to uskey liye her qadam par eik saal ke rozon aur qiyam ke amal ka sawab hai.''"
346,Hazrat Aus Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jisney Juma ke roz apna sar dhoya aur ghusl kya.'' aur misl saabiq riwayat bayan ki .
347,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se raawi hain ke aapney farmaya : '' jisney Juma ke roz ghusl kya aur apni ehliya ki khushbu istimal ki . agar uskey paas ho, aur apney umda kapdey pehney , phir logon ki gardanen na phalaangin aur waz ke beech mein (khutbey ke doran mein) koi laghw amal na kya, to ye ( Namaz ( un dono ( jumon (ke beech ke liye kaffara hogi aur jisney koi laghw kaam kya aur logon ki gardanen phalaangin to uskey liye ye Zohar hi hogi (yani Zohar ki Namaz ka sawab hoga na ke Jumey ka.'' ("
348,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne un se bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaar kamon (ki wajeh) se ghusl kya kartey they. janabat sey, Juma ke din, seengi lagwaaney se aur maiyat ko ghusl deney se .''"
349,Janab Ali bin Hoshab kehtey hain ke maine Mak-hool ( Shami Taabai ( se hadees ''غسل و اغتسل'' ke baarey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : us se murad ye hai ke jisney apna sar dhoya aur phir ghusl kya.
350,"Janab Saeed bin Abdul-Azeez (Tanukhi, taba Taabai) ne (غسل و اغتسل) ki sharah mein kaha ke jisney apna sar dhoya aur ghusl kya."
351,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney Juma ke din ghusle-janabat (ya janabat jaisa ghusl ( kya, phir Juma ke liye aaya to usney goya eik oont qurban kya. aur jo dusri sa'at mein aaya usney goya gaey qurban ki aur jo teesri sa'at mein pahuncha usney goya seengon wala mendha qurban kya. jo chauthi sa'at mein aaya usney goya murghi taqarrub ke liye pesh ki aur jo paanchwen sa'at mein aaya usney goya anda taqarrub ke liye pesh kya. phir jab Imam nikal aata hai to farishtey bhi zikr sunney ke liye hazir ho jatey hain.''"
352,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke log apney kaam kaaj khud hi sar-anjam diya kartey they aur apni usi haalat mein Juma ko chaley aatey they, to unhen kaha gaya ke agar tum ghusl kar liya karo (to bahut hi behtar hai.)"
353,"Janab Ikrima bayan kartey hain ke Iraq ki janib se kuch log aaye aur kehney lagey : aey ibne-Abbas ! kya aap Juma ke ghusl ko wajib kehtey hain? unhoney kaha : nahin lekin ye ziyada tahaarat ka baais hai aur jo ghusl kar ley uskey liye bahut behtar hai aur jo ghusl na karey us par wajib nahin hai. aur main tumhen batata hun ke ghusl kaisey shuru hua ? log mehnat w mashaqqat kya kartey they, libas oon ka hota tha, apni peethon par saman dhotey they aur unki masjid bhi tang aur neechi chhat wali thi , goya chhappar sa tha, to eik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye, din garm tha aur logon ko unke ooni libaason mein paseena aaya, yahan tak ke un se na-munasib badbuen niklin aur unhen eik doosrey se bahut taklif hui. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab ye bo mehsus ki to farmaya : ''logo! jab ye (Juma ka ( din hua karey to ghusl kya karo aur jisey jo umda tel aur khushbu mohaiyya ho istimal kya karey.'' ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : phir Allah taala ne halaat mein behtari paida kar di. log ooni libas chhod kar doosrey libas pehanney lagey aur mehnat mashaqqat ke kamon se bhi kifaayat ho gaee , masjid bhi khuli ho gaee aur wo paseena jo eik doosrey ke liye aziyat ka baais tha, khatam ho gaya."
354,Saiyedna Samra (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney wuzu kya usney sunnat par amal kya aur ye bahut umda sunnat hai. aur jisney ghusl kya to ye afzal hai.''
355,"Janab Khalifa bin Husain apney dada Hazrat Qais bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya, mein Islam qubul karna chahta tha. to aapney mujhey hukm diya ke main ghusl karun aur pani mein beri ke pattey miley huey hon."
356,Janab ibne-Juraij kehtey hain ke mujhey Aseem bin ( Kaseer bin ( Kulaib se khabar di gaee wo apney walid se wo unke dada se riwayat kartey hain ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur kaha ke maine Islam qubul kar liya hai aapney farmaya : '' apney kufr waley baal utaar do .'' yani sar mundao . aur) Kulaib kehtey hain ke) mujhey eik doosrey sahabi ne khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik doosrey shakhs se farmaya jo unke sath tha : '' apney kufr ke baal door karo aur khatna karao .''
357,"Muaza kehti hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke haaiza ke kapdon ko khoon lag jata hai) to kya karey ? ( unhoney kaha ke usey dhoey . agar uska nishan baqi rahey to kuch zardi ( waras buti ya Zaafran ( se usey tabdeel kar dey . kehti hain ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan teen teen haiz aatey they, magar main apna koi kapda na dhoti thi."
358,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham Rasul ki biviyon ke liye mehaz eik eik hi kapda hota tha, usi mein ayyame-haiz guzartey they. agar kahin koi khoon ka dhabba lag jata to wo usey apney luaab se geela karti aur phir usey mal deti thi."
359,"Janab Bakkaar bin Yahya kehtey hain ke mujh se meri daadi ne bayan kya ke main ummul-momenin Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan gaee , wahan un se eik Quraishi aurat ne puchha ke haiz waley kapdon mein Namaz ka kya hukm hai? to umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne jawab diya ke hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein haiz aata tha, ham ye din guzaartin aur phir paak hotin aur apney kapdey ko dekhtin jis mein ye din guzaarey hotey. agar usey khoon laga hota to usey dho letin aur phir us mein Namaz padhtin aur agar usey kuch na laga hota to usey usi tarah rehney detin aur us mein Namaz padhney se hamarey liye kuch maane (rukawat) na hota tha. aur jiskey baal goondhey huey hotey to jab kisi ko ghusl (janabat) karna hota to apney baal na khola karti balke apney sar par teen lap pani daalti. jab dekhti ke baalon ki jadein tar ho gaee hain to unhen malti phir baqi jism par pani baha leti."
360,Sayeda Asma binte-abi Bakar (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine eik aurat ko suna wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se poochh rahi thi ke jab ham mein se koi paak ho to apney kapdey ka kya karey? kya us mein Namaz padh liya karey? aapney farmaya : ''usey dekhey agar us mein khoon laga ho to usey pani laga kar khurchey aur jis jagah kuch nazar na aata ho (magar shubha ho to ( wahan chheentey maar ley aur us mein Namaz padh ley.''
361,"Sayeda Asma binte-abi Bakr (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke eik aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha , usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! farmaiye ke jab ham mein se kisi ke kapdey ko haiz ka khoon lag jaey to kaisey karey ? aapney farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ke kapdey ko haiz ka khoon lag jaey, to chahiye ke usey khurchey, ( chutkiyon se ragdey ( phir us par pani daley. aur us mein Namaz padh ley.''"
362,"Esa bin Yunus aur Hammad bin Salma dono ne mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya aur kaha : ''usey ukhedo , pani dal kar chutkiyon se ragdo phir ( mazeed (pani bahao .''"
363,Hazrat umme-Qais binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se haiz ke khoon ke mutalliq puchha jo ke kapdey ko lag jata hai. aapney farmaya : ''usey kisi lakdi se ukhedo phir beri ke pattey miley pani se dho dalo .''
364,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmati hain ke ham Rasul ki biviyon mein se her eik ke paas eik kurta hi hua karta tha. usi mein ayyame-haiz guzartey , usi mein janabat hoti , phir agar us mein khoon ka qatra dekhti to usey luaab laga kar malti (aur uska izaala kar deti .)"
365,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Khaula binte-Yasar (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan ayen aur kehney lagen : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey paas sirf eik hi kapda hai aur mujhey us mein haiz aata hai, to kaisey kya karun ? aapney farmaya : ''jab tum paak hua karo to usey dho liya karo aur us mein Namaz padha karo.'' wo kehney lagin ke agar us se khoon (ka nishan ( na nikley to ? farmaya : '' tumhen khoon ka dho dalna kafi hai. uskey dagh aur nishan ka koi harj nahin .''"
366,"Hazrat Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni behen ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us kapdey mein Namaz padh liya kartey they jis mein wo sohbat kartey they? unhoney kaha : haan , agar us mein koi gandagi na hoti ."
367,"ummul-momenin Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey kapdon ya lihaafon mein Namaz na padha kartey they. (yani aam taur se ( Ubaidullah ne kaha : '' ( شعرنا أو في لحفنا ( '' ke alfaz mein merey walid ko shak hua hai."
368,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey lihaafon mein Namaz nahin padha kartey they. Hammad ne kaha : maine Saeed bin abi Sadqa se suna, wo kehtey they ke maine Muhammad bin Sirin se is hadees ke baarey mein puchha to unhoney mujhey ye hadees bayan nahin ki . aur kaha ke maine usey eik muddat pehley suna tha, maloom nahin kis se suna tha, wo qabile-bharosa tha ya nahin. tum doosrey ulama se uski tehqiq kar lo."
369,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padhi , aap eik kambal odhey huey they jiska kuch hissey aap par aur kuch unki ehliya par tha aur wo haiz se thin aap us haalat mein Namaz padhtey rahey ke wo aap par tha."
370,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko Namaz padhtey aur main aap ke paas bazu ( pehlu ( mein hoti aur haiz se hoti , mujh par jo chadar ya kambal hota uska kuch hissey aap bhi liye huey hotey they."
371,Hammam bin Haris kehtey hain ke wo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan ( bator mehman ( aaye huey they ke unhen ehtilaam ho gaya. wo kapdey se ehtilaam ka nishan dho rahey they ya kapda dho rahey they ke Hazrat Aaysha ki londi ne unhen dekh liya . usney ja kar Hazrat Aaysha ko bataya to unhoney kaha : mujhey khoob yaad hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kapdey se usey khurch dala karti thi. is riwayat ko Aamash ne bhi riwayat kya jaisey ke hukm ne riwayat kya hai.
372,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kapdey se mani ko khurch dala karti thi aur phir aap usi mein Namaz padh liya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Mughira , abu-Maashar aur Waasil ne Hammad bin abi Suleman ki muwaafiqat ki hai."
373,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kapdey se mani ko dho diya karti thin. wo kehti hain ke phir main dekhti ke kapdey par) dhoney ke) nishan numaya hotey .
374,"Hazrat umme-Qais binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke wo apney eik chhotey bachey ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein laain. usney abhi khana khana shuru nahin kya tha. aapney usey apni god mein bitha liya, pas usney aap ke kapdey par peshab kar diya to aapney pani mangwaya aur us par chhidak diya aur usey dhoya nahin."
375,Sayeda Lubaba bint Haris (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki god mein they ke peshab kar diya to maine kaha ke aap doosra kapda pehan lein aur ye chadar mujhey de-den ke usey dho dun. aapney farmaya : '' sirf ladki ka peshab hi dhoya jata hai aur ladkey ke peshab par chheentey maarey jatey hain.''
376,"Hazrat Abu-Samah (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat kya karta tha. aap jab ghusl karna chahtey to mujhey farmatey : ''meri taraf apni guddi ( pusht ( kar lo.'' to main aapki taraf guddi karkey khada ho jata aur aap ko is tarah parda karta. ( eik baar ( Hazrat Hasan ya Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko laya gaya to unhoney aap ke seeney par peshab kar diya. main usey dhoney aaya to aapney farmaya : '' ladki ka peshab dhoya jata hai aur ladkey ke peshab par chheentey maarey jatey hain.'' Abbas (bin Abdul-Azeem ( ne apni sanad mein) حدثني mufrad ke seedhey ke bajaey ( حدثنا Yahya bin Walid zikr kya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain, aur wo abu-Zara hai aur Harun bin Tameem ne Janab Hasan Basri se naqal kya hai ke peshab sab barabar hain."
377,Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke ladki ka peshab dhoya jaey aur ladkey ke peshab par chheentey maarey jaeyn jab tak ke khana na khata ho.
378,"Saiyedna Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. phir mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya hai, magar us mein : ''jab tak ke khana na khata ho.'' ka bayan nahin hai, magar ye izafa kya hai ke Qatada ne kaha : ye hukm us waqt tak hai jabke wo dono (ladka, ladki) khana na khatey hon. jab khana khaney lag jaeyn to dono ka peshab dhoya jaey."
379,"Janab Hasan Basri apni walida se raawi hain wo bayan karti hain ke unhoney Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ko dekha ke wo ladkey ke peshab par chheentey maatin jab tak ke wo khana na khata, jab khana khaney lagta to usko dhoti thin aur ladki ke peshab ko dhoti thin."
380,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik badwi ( dehati ( masjid mein aaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma they, usney aa kar Namaz padhi . ibne-Abda ne kaha ke do rakatein padhein . phir ye dua ki : ( اللهم ارحمني . ... ( ''aey Allah ! mujh par aur Muhammad par rehem kar aur hamarey sath kisi par rehem na kar .'' is par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tune to wasee aur kushada ko tang kar diya hai.'' (yani Allah ki rehmat ko.) phir ziyada der na guzri ke wo masjid ke koney mein peshab kerney laga , log jaldi se uski taraf badhey , magar aapney unko rok diya aur farmaya : ''tum log aasani kerney waley bana kar bhejey gaey ho dushwaari waley nahin. us ( peshab ( par pani ka eik dol dal do .'' raawi ko shak hai ke (سجلا من ماء) ke lafz ada kiye ya (ذنوبا من ماء) ke .) maani dono ka eik hi hai. ("
381,Janab Abdullah bin Maaqil bin Muqrin (Rahimahullah) ( Taabai ( bayan kartey hain ke eik badwi ( dehati ( ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi aur mazkura baala qissa bayan kya. us riwayat mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis jagah usney peshab kya hai usey khurch do aur pani baha do .'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye hadees mursal hai (yani Taabai ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat ki hai.) aur Abdullah bin Maaqil ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko nahin paya hai.
382,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein main masjid mein soyaa karta tha. meri bharpur jawani ke din they aur abhi shaadi nahin hui thi. kuttey masjid mein aatey jatey aur peshab bhi kar detey they magar wo log (yani Sahaba kiram (us par koi pani na chhidaktey they.
383,Ibrahim bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ki eik umme-walad Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ummul-momenin se riwayat karti hain ke unhoney puchha ke main aisi aurat hun ke apni chadar ko lamba rakhti hun aur) kabhi ( raah chaltey huey najas jagah se bhi guzar hota hai) aur chadar ka pallu us par se ho kar guzarta hai) to umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' baad wali jagah usey paak kar deti hai.''
384,"Musa bin Abdullah bin Yazid bano Abdul-Ash'hal ki eik khatoon se riwayat kartey hain wo bayan karti hain ke maine kaha aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamara masjid mein janey ka raasta ganda hai, jab barish ho jaey to ham kya keren? aapney farmaya : ''kya us (najas) jagah ke baad paak jagah nahin aati? ''maine kaha ke haan (aati hai) aapney farmaya : ''to ye uskey badley hai.''"
385,"Janab Saeed bin abi Saeed Maqbari ne apney walid se bayan kya, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apney jootey se gandagi ko raundey to mitti usey paak kerney wali hai.''"
386,"Janab Saeed bin abi Saeed apney walid sey, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya. us riwayat mein hai : ''jab koi apney mozon se gandagi ko raundey to mitti usey paak kerney wali hai.''"
387,"Janab Saeed bin abi Saeed , Qaaqaa bin Hakim se wo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya."
388,"umme-Yunus binte-Shaddad kehti hain ke mujh se meri nand umme-Jahdar Aamiriya ne bayan kya ke unhoney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se haiz ke khoon ke mutalliq puchha jo kapdey ko lag jata hai to unhoney kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath thi , ham par hamara kapda tha, uskey ooper ham ne eik ooni chadar dali hui thi , jab subh hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ooper wali chadar odh li aur Namaz ke liye tashrif ley gaey aur Fajr ki Namaz padhi , phir beth rahey . eik aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye khoon ka dagh hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chadar ke us hissey ko jis par dagh tha pakad liya , aur eik ghulam ko de-kar merey paas bheja aur farmaya : ''usey dho kar khushk karo aur merey paas wapis bhej do .'' chunanche maine apna piyala mangwaya , us chadar ko dhoya aur khushk karkey aap ke paas wapis bhej diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do-pehar ke waqt tashrif laye to aap wo chadar odhey huey they."
389,Janab abu-Nazara (Rahimahullah) ( Taabai ( bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney kapdey mein thooka aur phir usey us mein masal diya. ( ye riwayat mursal hai)
390,"Humaid ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ke misl riwayat kya."
